TextBody: Discover new businesses - Network - Learn - Find investment opportunities & much more [https://mcusercontent.com/26d042a197a4ad7c910d8818a/images/5d16aa3a-aa15-1abb-bce9-513b7cef237a.jpeg] <https://halalexpolondon.us8.list-manage.com/track/click?u=26d042a197a4ad7c910d8818a&id=c34c9bf313&e=567d760780> [https://mcusercontent.com/26d042a197a4ad7c910d8818a/images/69a24bbd-fd87-5abc-2e7f-5ccf2e2c85a9.jpeg] <https://halalexpolondon.us8.list-manage.com/track/click?u=26d042a197a4ad7c910d8818a&id=36fe8ae8ed&e=567d760780> Amir Khan supports Halal Expo Manchester in the development of Muslim-led businesses and entrepreneurs We are pleased to announce The Amir Khan Foundation as our official charity partner for Halal Expo Manchester and Halal Expo London. The foundation is committed to a number of worthy charitable causes in the UK and internationally, such as helping to alleviate food poverty and emergency disaster relief with ongoing support in severely affected areas. We are grateful for the recognition from the foundation for our work in providing a platform for Muslim businesses, entrepreneurs & professionals where they can discover opportunities for trade, investment & networking. We continue to work in uniting manufacturers & suppliers with buyers and consumers in the UK and international halal industry. Join us in discovering the latest halal products & services on 14th & 15th July at Old Trafford Stadium. Book Your Stand Now<https://halalexpolondon.us8.list-manage.com/track/click?u=26d042a197a4ad7c910d8818a&id=714e4b4a3b&e=567d760780> [https://mcusercontent.com/26d042a197a4ad7c910d8818a/images/0284332c-52aa-d3ea-50c2-edcb22f52324.jpg] <https://halalexpolondon.us8.list-manage.com/track/click?u=26d042a197a4ad7c910d8818a&id=bb2d83554a&e=567d760780> Showcase & Sell Your Products and Services Uniting Manufacturers & Suppliers with Buyers & Consumers If you are looking to raise your brand awareness, launching a new business, seeking professional insights, networking or investment opportunities register to exhibit your brand now.

Subject: Take advantage of the Food and Hospitality Oman exhibition to unlock business growth potential
TextBody: Dear Industry Colleague, With the Food and Hospitality Oman (FHO)<https://info.foodandhospitalityoman.com/c/110Ca5tMI9lkePHj8VpmZ46VrF> quickly approaching, we wanted to take this opportunity to remind you of the great opportunities available for your business to take part in this event. Through FHO<https://info.foodandhospitalityoman.com/c/110CaNmzvTo8JttvfqGGQ2RGre> you will increase your business' visibility to over 6,000 attendees by showcasing your products and services, and networking with leading industry professionals from a growth market. FHO is organized under the patronage of Oman Ministry of Agriculture, Fisheries Wealth and Water Resources and engage stakeholders through FHO Knowledge Hub, an activation event that includes a Forum, B2B Matchmaking and product demonstrations. The food and hospitality industry in Oman is growing steadily, according to Statista, revenue in the Food segment is projected to reach US$333.70m in 2023 and is expected to show an annual growth rate (CAGR 2023-2027) of 16.05%. On other side, revenue in the Hotels segment is projected to reach US$197m in 2023 and is expected to show an annual growth rate (CAGR 2023-2027) of 6.20%, resulting in a projected market volume of US$250.70m by 2027. Prime locations are selling out fast, take advantage of this limited time offer and secure the perfect spot for your business today.

Subject: DOBAR DAN
TextBody: Pozdrav Moje ime je advokat David Richard, advokat ovdje u UK. Znam da je ovo bez presedana, ali vjerujem da postoji prilika u ovakvim vremenima. Postoji nepretražena polisa trajnog životnog osiguranja koju drži moj pokojni klijent, a transakcija se odnosi na nepotraženi štedni novčani depozit 'plativi na smrt' u iznosu od 17.820.000,00 funti (sedamnaest miliona osamsto dvadeset hiljada britanskih funti) banka. Vlasnik police bio je jedan od naših klijenata koji slučajno ima isto prezime kao i vaše, a koji je radio sa energetskom kompanijom ovdje u UK, umro je od raka. Od njegove smrti niko se nije javio da podnese zahtjev i svi naši napori da pronađemo njegove rođake su se pokazali neuspješnima. On nema ženu i djecu. Kodeks osiguravajućeg društva propisuje da se 'osigurane trajne polise' koje se ne traže moraju predati državnoj podjeli za napuštenu imovinu nakon 8 godina. Tražim vašu saglasnost da budete u partnerstvu sa mnom za pravo na ovu polisu, s obzirom na činjenicu da dijelite isto ime sa preminulim. Ako mi dozvolite da dodam vaše ime u polisu, sav prihod će biti obrađen u vaše ime. Želim da istaknem da želim da 10% ovog novca bude podijeljeno među dobrotvorne organizacije, dok ćemo preostalih 90% podijeliti među nama. Podnošenjem ove tvrdnje nećemo prekršiti nijedan zakon jer imam svu potrebnu dokumentaciju da ubrzam proces na visokoprofesionalan i povjerljiv način. Ja ću obezbijediti svu relevantnu dokumentaciju da potkrijepim svoj zahtjev kao korisnika. Ova tvrdnja zahtijeva visok nivo povjerljivosti, vaš najraniji odgovor na ovo pitanje bi bio vrlo cijenjen. razmotrite ovu ponudu i pošaljite mi svoje podatke kako slijedi za dokumentaciju 1, njihova puna imena, 2, vaša kontakt adresa / država prebivališta, 3, vaš direktni broj mobilnog telefona 4, datum rođenja 5, vaše zanimanje S poštovanjem, Advokat David Richard

Subject: RFQ
TextBody: Dear Axelle, I would like to express my sincere appreciation for your quick response to my recent query. Your promptness in addressing my concerns has been immensely helpful and I am grateful for your timely assistance. Thank you once again for your exceptional support. I hope i have answered all your queries. * Do you already purchase frozen (potato) products? What is your experience in this field? * A-Yes we do have. From last 3 years we have been doing this * If yes, with what brands or companies do you already work? Why do you wish to change? * A-We used to deal majorly with indian brands like Balagi foods, Fumwave etc * Do you have your own distribution channel and warehouses? * A-Our company is situated in dubai and we cover Mena and african regions. We Have a wearhouse but its for a differnt business, we are also in production of arabic snacks which we supply for 5 star hotels. * What is your market strategy? Who are your customers? * A-As we are in meat business our client also buy these kinds of items like french fries, wedges, hash browns etc. The statergy is to cross sell other items. * Are you active in multiple countries? Since your company is located in the UAE, but your request is for Senegal? * A-As i mentioned we are active in Mena region and African countries in quite sometime now. We look forward to hearing from you soon.

TextBody: Hello Axelle, That's right, we were at the PLMA fair and had the chance to meet you at your booth. Anton is great! Subject: Warehouse Automation: Revolutionizing Supply Chain Management
TextBody: In this email, you will learn more about warehouse automation. ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ [https://content.app-us1.com/cdn-cgi/image/dpr=2,fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,width=650/WYkQG/2021/07/16/e3fd5507-7b71-4423-9b63-56ab23d2de91.png?r=965523381] Hello! Supply chain management has been affected by technological advancements in recent years just like many other industries. Through the use of automation technologies, warehouse operations have undergone a remarkable transformation. Supply chain management has gone through a revolution due to warehouse automation, which has increased productivity, accuracy, and efficiency. Let’s look at how warehouse automation is changing the supply chain landscape. * The increased efficiency it brings to supply chain operations is one of the most important benefits of warehouse automation. Numerous tasks in the warehouse have been simplified by automation technologies like robotic systems, automated conveyors, and sorting equipment. * The enhanced accuracy - Automation in the warehouse significantly lowers the possibility of human error. Because errors are less likely to occur as a result of this accuracy, customer satisfaction increases and the number of returns and replacements declines. * Inventory Optimization - Automated systems are able to track item locations, continuously track stock levels, and provide real-time data on inventory status. Organizations can use this information to make informed choices about demand forecasting, storage allocation, and inventory replenishment. Want to learn more? Subject: PROPOSAL
TextBody: Good Day, My name is Sgt.Helen William am an American soldier serving in Syria.I have some money i would like to invest in your country. Please get back to me if you are interested.Once I hear from you,I will give you details concerning the funds. Thank you. Sgt.Helen William.

Subject: Meeting request/ Business proposal
TextBody: Dear sales manager, I am the Managing Director of Ali Walad Wady Company, a family business in the food industry based in the Sultanate of Oman. I would like to expand my business to include the famous Belgian fries. For this end I will be travelling to Belgium on the 10th of June for a period of one week to discuss partnership possibilities and conclude agreements with your renowned company in the potato market. The initial plan is to import around 4 - 6 containers of frozen French fries annually. If this business proposal interests you, I would kindly request scheduling a meeting at your earliest convenience, taking into account my availability in the abovementioned period. For more information, Mr. Wadi can be reached on : Email: a.waladwadi@hotmail.com Mobile: +968 9124 6094 Looking forward to doing business with your company, Sincerely yours, Suha DAAS, Executive Assistant in Belgium Email: Suha_68@yahoo.com Mobile: +32 (0) 484 29.19.69

Subject: Project Qatar 2023 wraps up with great success
TextBody: The latest business news from throughout the Middle East [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/bb28bf55-0765-d3a1-b314-5fc79ed1da7e.png]<https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=8ddb708a66&e=0b771b35a1> June 2nd, 2023 [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/7e6d0440-8da2-9200-b047-06d9997f7fad.png] <https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=df185d0a22&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/dfd9178c-5787-4748-10e7-ca40fbe85766.jpeg] Project Qatar 2023 wraps up with great success The 19th edition of Project Qatar, the highly anticipated international trade exhibition showcasing construction materials, equipment, and technology, was officially inaugurated on the 29th of May by HE Sheikh Mohammed bin Hamad bin Qassim Al-Abdullah Al-Thani, Minister of Commerce and Industry of Qatar. FULL ARTICLE<https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=3b7945a17e&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/e3b55357-33d1-edc1-8ec5-7838e84617c0.png] Qatar’s non-oil sector achieved 9.9% growth in Q4 2022: Prime Minister Al Thani said the nation's efforts have led to the establishment of strong financial institutions and the creation of the foundations for a work environment that encourages the growth of business. FULL ARTICLE<https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=55db3446dd&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/35da5b90-5d21-a180-e49c-1144dca100f9.jpg] Saudi Arabia offers 50 investment opportunities worth over $25bn in machinery, equipment sector Saudi Minister of Industry and Mineral Resources Bandar Alkhorayef said these investment opportunities are being developed and raised on the Invest Saudi platform to activate the National Industry Strategy. FULL ARTICLE<https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=7cbeab2faa&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/fa362b05-e0fb-8e2f-4d43-edebad5eea86.jpg] Oman gears up for its first smart city Oman has officially joined the race towards smart cities with the Sultanate’s first smart city project, in line with Oman Vision 2040. Sultan Haitham City will cover an area of 15 million m2 in Al Seeb city, northwest of Muscat. FULL ARTICLE<https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=fd31331a53&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/e044200b-52ad-c6b3-d2d8-5573d849d1a6.jpg] <https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=0586365491&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/df2b0d0a-4d2c-de80-f9b2-099a5c2abf66.png] Qatar to implement new strategies for real estate development The first phase will include data and information that will be provided to those concerned. The data will include occupancy volumes and deals in different regions, as well as information of interest to individuals and investors in general. FULL ARTICLE<https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=cd5cde58e3&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/8ac4d2a6-fbbe-47aa-7671-a0762ec2e8d9.jpg] Egypt’s agriculture exports rise 17.2 percent in 5 months Egypt’s agriculture exports increased to 3.4 million tons during the period from January until 17 May, a 17.2 percent increase over the same period in 2022, according to a report by the Ministry of Agriculture and Land Reclamation. FULL ARTICLE<https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=e31c5611e9&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/c7b49c19-110e-a161-9010-55fc27032552.png] <https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=f0bb0c5638&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/ae7b7aba-7556-385c-8871-1e53a134aeb0.png] <https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=4ea9206865&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/bcbbc886-93b7-ded7-2fee-4ac1d6d87c77.png] Fitch revises outlook on Oman to positive; affirms at ‘BB’ The Positive Outlook reflects lower government debt/GDP, with high oil prices and spending restraint reducing external liquidity risk. FULL ARTICLE<https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=fd894f03a3&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/29a837bf-3c34-1e4d-d86e-94082e948623.jpg] Saudi-US trade and investment volume hits $55bn, US Embassy in Riyadh reveals Trade between the US and Saudi Arabia has rocketed by 122 percent since 2021, according to new figures released by the North American country’s embassy in Riyadh. FULL ARTICLE<https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=dfe40b78fb&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/ab8a8cda-5d47-cac5-894c-91642283a844.jpg] <https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=5851d775d9&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/4ff3c06b-4052-9ffc-81a0-32456dbd5acc.png] Qatar: Over 700 hotel keys added in Q1 The supply of hotel rooms has continued to increase in Qatar over the first three months of 2023, with more than 700 keys were added to the market between January and March. FULL ARTICLE<https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=0d35983ebf&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/551cb865-30e1-8d7a-85f6-bee95bfd42d4.jpg] <https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=c1846b7528&e=0b771b35a1> Egypt secures $66 mln from EU, AFD to expand wheat storage The loan is part of a €225 million initiative to improve food security in North Africa, of which €100 million has been allocated for Egypt to help meet its wheat and grain needs. FULL ARTICLE<https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=76d5690391&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/6879c578-db6a-47ce-d4e6-820303e9a441.jpg] <https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=a015befe42&e=0b771b35a1> Oman’s refinery products output jumps by 44% Total refinery products in the Sultanate of Oman grew by 44 per cent at the end of February 2023, compared to the same period in 2022, according to preliminary statistics issued by the National Centre for Statistics and Information (NCSI). FULL ARTICLE<https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=19f0eb3114&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/020cd112-2919-810a-2478-85078ab3fa75.png] <https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=32643ed5a1&e=0b771b35a1> [https://mcusercontent.com/6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c/images/629e61d9-4bd4-739f-2233-949df58fd70b.jpg] <https://ifpgroup.us1.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6bd76116d198fe5839fc7271c&id=4a4abed5b7&e=0b771b35a1> Value of Saudi construction contracts jump 35% to $51.3bn: report The USSBC said the overall deals struck between October and December were the highest since the first quarter of 2015, when contract values touched SR88.1 billion. Subject: PLMA meeting follow up!
TextBody: Dear Zahia, Thank you for your prompt reply! I have some questions which I would like to address before analyzing and advance our discussion. 1. Maestro brand will be offer only to us or you as commodity product its available for other companies which may have an inquiry in the future 2. On the offer which you have sent on the quality part I see to types: FS and R1, what they support to mean? 3. FCA terms and prepayment in the beginning is acceptable for us, are these the final prices as I would really to ask for you to check if any additional support at least for the first couple of orders. 4. The lead time of 4 weeks, is this a usual time of preparing an order or due to the season? Thank you once again and looking forward to hear from you. Gjithë të mirat/

Subject: SUPPLY CHAIN: CHINA AND RUSSIA TAKE STEPS TO STRENGTHEN TRADE
TextBody: [email-image] SUPPLY CHAIN: CHINA AND RUSSIA TAKE STEPS TO STRENGTHEN TRADE Russia expects trade with China to reach a record US$ 200 billion by 2023, while the war launched against Ukraine drags on, the Kremlin strengthens its relations with China. The Russian Prime Minister, Mikhail Mishustin, arrived this May 24 in Beijing where he held a meeting with President Xi Jinping and signed a series of commercial agreements with which Moscow aims to strengthen its finances. The Asian nation is on track to be the largest buyer of the food staple this season. And while Beijing said last year that it would allow imports from all parts of Russia, trade has been hampered by a slew of issues, these include phytosanitary regulations and transport challenges, Russia's main wheat-growing area is in the south near the Black Sea, a long way from China [facebook-social-icon]<https://u20443185.ct.sendgrid.net/ls/click?upn=q1hVHtzpZQ2t9ewsYKor-2F6ON9nOzUgjV19icIJTstOCZbMK8Y1Wsc4JI8hK0j6wufNfnJFYkooXAz-2Bdl750E94fcWEX-2FJ6fI7szZFA1BKbM-3D9ACl_xu5RDHlEaGQfNLU5cwDJxmPEJ487GSucy7SAelbBb2P7BqWXwAhhbSCMcYXVHkQq4-2FF5cn3EsB7ijsFkLpy-2FiSJloZ0yJz91U7bosS1-2BkKi7DcYxgPpZfyHX1XMt3xdkNkoH-2FtICNVkJwsDDyYberAVpucqc5mBGl7AvBzJx-2Bnk0FaImJ7h997OZzXXrMRgr2xxfLi7HJGgADvAhQb0pQ-2BfY7sYuOgh6A5Ldn-2BtFBWKTFAEUYUCy3QwaorjuFctvKzUm4-2BJFk4Tttkxqt83BPBLKlHQVhMSMmyX1mDfQAqc-3D> [linkedin-social-icon] <https://u20443185.ct.sendgrid.net/ls/click?upn=q1hVHtzpZQ2t9ewsYKor-2F27AiBFvtO7iUn2blcM-2Bp-2B6VOBGtFyJvjsmAbp-2F6hs-2FgCfob9cSpGG7tIEOxKw7xo-2FcgfSFO0vb3HsmetY8gVTlP8sD6L2r8X4jf4RdNwBd1iz-2FvT4y1AV2Oh2MjiE4MKQ-3D-3Dekyo_xu5RDHlEaGQfNLU5cwDJxmPEJ487GSucy7SAelbBb2P7BqWXwAhhbSCMcYXVHkQq4-2FF5cn3EsB7ijsFkLpy-2FiSJloZ0yJz91U7bosS1-2BkKi7DcYxgPpZfyHX1XMt3xdkNkoH-2FtICNVkJwsDDyYberJxC6z5bEMWU5TWKToxwEKckPO1tAIFnP5sev5rNchcR74IzhLZhI7QnV6n-2Bc-2F1BlNg-2FnLNO-2F1zAiXcYc20Zm7M4wyIuMI3Q9A-2FFnVBTxfRJyALWqIUDl4iVAmxH0THqN2Zz6Zh1OVGn4xvjrN2oQAw-3D> [instagram-social-icon] <https://u20443185.ct.sendgrid.net/ls/click?upn=q1hVHtzpZQ2t9ewsYKor-2F-2BNRO4hGuNB31-2BYEr1t-2BqV6x6j6PC8J5yKjTGPiiqzKYI3BvF62F0zKwfb26CXS1ag-3D-3DbjFh_xu5RDHlEaGQfNLU5cwDJxmPEJ487GSucy7SAelbBb2P7BqWXwAhhbSCMcYXVHkQq4-2FF5cn3EsB7ijsFkLpy-2FiSJloZ0yJz91U7bosS1-2BkKi7DcYxgPpZfyHX1XMt3xdkNkoH-2FtICNVkJwsDDyYberGbDGlr7hK6DXp5i2XNSz5x4YhyjRhUH6dHnYbKzN8mB7lCbeCi-2B4rDgHn1fClB7jUB0-2BTago0-2BIx54Aa-2BDAnhyonFswGeocfXrH8ma324TQqx4F-2FGO8qgBsSAYNSXkgwXxa27iFpkjQKbKXbbbffoY-3D> This email was sent to Sales@agristo.com by pati@bbcommodities.com. Subject: Offer of cooperation
TextBody: Dear Sir/Madame, Please allow me to introduce you to our company. For more than 30 years Fótimpex-MPI Ltd. has been designing and constructing exhibition stands, complete exhibitions and community stands all over Europe. Whether your idea is for a simple, modular stand or a half-custom or complex custom-built stand, we can certainly help you with everything from design to manufacture to on-site assembly, and we can also take care of the dismantling for you. We also specialise in furniture manufacturing and interior design. Please have a look at the attached reference works and our website and if you see the possibility of a future cooperation, do not hesitate to contact me!
Did you receive my letter ?

Subject: contract supply
TextBody: Dear Supplier, I Greet you from Republic of Kazakhstan. Please there is a supply demand in your line of products and I would like to send you a request for quotation. Kindly send us your brochure or product catalog and price details. My name is Mr. Malik Hussein, from Malikhussein Trading Company Limited. We are licensed business consultants in Kazakhstan involved in import and export business. We are seeking to represent foreign companies like manufacturers, suppliers or distributors who wish to have a presence and supply their products in Kazakhstan and UAE as there is demand for your products which is among the products needed for the supply. The Board is in collaboration with the United Arab Emirates (UAE) Authority for a smooth payment and shipment/delivery of goods. We hope this could be a start for a long term business relationship with your company. Waiting to hear from you. Thank You ----------------------

Subject: PRESENTATIONS OF INTERCOP
TextBody: Dear Sir/Madam, INTERCOP, provides national and international complete logistic services incorporating air, sea, rail and land transport, full warehousing and distribution facilities, container and related intermodal and global supporting services that supports the Freight Forwarding Wing. [Europa y África en globo terráqueo]Global Operations: Operations & Custom Clearance: end to end logistic services with and under a single point of contact. [Camión]Specialized Transport Logistic: Rapid and effective to move cargo from port to warehouse and /or directly to your customers. Services can be combined or tailored to meet individual client´s needs. Traditional Container & Pallets Transport: Specialized logistic handling and delivery of any products, services include transportation and logistics container management. Warehousing and storage for food grade, hazardous & non-hazardous goods, land, sea and air freight delivery. [Escena de puente]Seamless end to end cross docking facilities: Solutions for quick perfect dispatch Solutions for any unique or abnormal/wide-load and fragile items. Warehousing: [Carro]Spacious own warehouse and machineries with all modes of distributions makes our warehouse synergies the best in the business. Thank you for having taken the time to read our presentation. Waiting to hear and be at your service in a very near future. P.S. Intercop has started on a new project due to urge of clients that want to send things back home via Groupage Service, and we wonder if you would like to participate with other cargo agents at your side, that would send them to the Canaries to be re-routed to African Countries.

Subject: Basmati Rice Private Label.
TextBody: Greetings from Minar Foods Inc ! We are a FSSC 22000 approved processor and exporter of Basmati rice with a core specialization of provisioning private labels for esteemed retailers and wholesalers. Our production facility and quality assurance standard duly stands approved on Food safety grounds for provisioning of private labels by the likes of Majid Al Futtaim Carrefour, Markaz Sultan, Geant, Safeway & Americana who are all a part of our elite customer base. Our own Minar Brand range is also being exported to more than twenty two countries around the globe and for us It will be an honour to get associated with your esteemed organization as a reliable supplier of a top quality rice brand which has been immaculately processed as per prime food safety standards. Attached to this email you may please find our corporate profile. Your valued feedback regarding the future line of action will be eagerly awaited.

Subject: Don't Miss Out on the Biggest International Trade Show for the Food and Hospitality Industry in Oman!
TextBody: Dear Industry Colleague, The largest international trade show for the food and hospitality industry in Oman is less than a few months away; Food and Hospitality Oman (FHO)<https://info.foodandhospitalityoman.com/c/110EGvLK1hnlQlr0Lb2Ldk26Jd>, 18-20 September 2023. Among the countries participating at this year’s event include Belgium, India, Iran, Qatar, Pakistan, Thailand, Turkey, and the UAE. Multiple leading brands have already confirmed their participation, including A'Saffa, the official poultry sponsor, Gulf Mushrooms, INOX Kitchen Equipment, to only mention a few. Among the supporters of FHO are Ministry of Agriculture, Fisheries Wealth and Water Resources Oman, Abu Dhabi Department of Economic Development, the PHD Chamber of Commerce of India, and the Trade Development Authority of Pakistan. Exhibitors and sponsors at FHO can expect to meet senior level decision makers and purchasers across hoteliers, food and beverage suppliers, food supply chain managers, retailers, restauranters, hotels managers, chefs, and investors and entrepreneurs in the food and hospitality industry. FHO<https://info.foodandhospitalityoman.com/c/110EHdEwP1qakZdcRGk54iMRIM> is an excellent opportunity for your company to explore growth potential by displaying your products, equipment, and services to a highly qualified audience. Contact me today to confirm your participation. +968 9207 9800 or roni.barua@connectthroughus.com<mailto:roni.barua@connectthroughus.com>

A business solution is the practice of developing various aspects of business functions through multiple techniques and strategies. The key goal of a business solution is to promote the elements of a brand along with the qualities or benefits of a product or a service. Business solutions are not only developing your business operations but also expressing your brand values through as many as approaches possible. With the right approach, business solutions connect your values with the right audiences that need added value. Business solutions help you discover the target market, which is the fundamental step in marketing. Whenever implementing various business solutions, keep in mind that you will find out who your customers are, as you can modify the elements of your services or products according to their exact needs. It can also make you focus on a niche market, and you can create a brand identity based on their hopes, behaviours, desires, cultures, languages, and needs. Business solutions will also empower a brand to discover its competitive brands. It will not help you to imitate exactly what the existing brands are doing, but it will make you aware of what services and products competitors are offering now. If a brand wants to achieve something in the long run, discovering exact competitive brands is an inevitable step, which you will obtain with the right business solutions. Subject: Rental Exhibition Stands for Trade Fairs - - Competence in the Space of Time
TextBody: [cid:8CA6C5A56DE62EA1C417@ORBITAL] Dear Sir or Madam, our company would like to offer you planning, drawing and building of representative exhibition stands that attract a lot of visitors. Free of charge and non-binding: * Planning and design in accordance with your budget * Detailed price offer * Modified design according to your needs on demand If you are interested in our offer and you want to have an amazing stand, do not hesitate to contact us. Our project leaders look forward to receiving your call on our phone number: +420 568 821 130 or e-mail: orbital@orbital.eu.com. We would be pleased if you have an interesting stand for your fair just from us. The offered stand is suitable for the fair ANUGA.

Subject: Anuga 2023 vom 7. bis 11. Oktober 2023 in Köln anbieten.
TextBody: Ladies and Gentlemen, We would like to offer our full support to your company's participation in Anuga 2023, taking place in Cologne from October 7th to 11th, 2023. As a company with 2500m2 of indoor production and 2500m2 of outdoor storage space, we have been actively participating in trade fairs across European countries and fulfilling our customers' individual exhibition requirements with utmost satisfaction. Therefore, through our reliable and professional experts, we are providing you with a stress-free and successful exhibition stand. Of course, we can also design individual exhibition stands according to your specific requests. The provision of 3D projections and short film animations is complimentary. During the fair, we make on-site adjustments and assist you with stand installation, ensuring that we find solutions to any issues you may encounter. Due to the COVID-19 pandemic, we are in closer communication with the fair organizers regarding planning. We will assist you in complying with hygiene regulations by offering disinfection stations, gloves, sanitizers, or any other necessary items. We are always available to provide further information and look forward to hearing from you soon to work together successfully. Please note that this is not an advertisement but a request for a proposal for your exhibition stand.

Subject: Anuga - Food & Beverage Fair 2023 Attendees/Registrants List.
TextBody: Hi there, Hope you are doing well. Would you be interested in acquiring a list of attendees/registrants for your marketing initiatives. Show: Anuga - Food & Beverage Fair 2023. Counts: 71,883 Details Included: Company name, Contact name, Title, Address, Website, Phone number, Fax number, Verified email address, Employee size, and Revenue size, SIC code, Industry type etc.. If you feel this might bring some changes in your business growth, we will be happy to send samples and additional information for your review. Looking forward for your response.

Very good Review score 4.5 from 15 to 17 of September Karen Demirchyan Complex | Yerevan, Armenia Participate in the exhibition! The main exhibition of the region ARMENIA EXPO has long and firmly established the position of the largest, authoritative, most anticipated and significant event in the business life of not only Armenia, but the entire region. Every year, the exhibition brings together the largest manufacturers from Armenia, Russia, Iran, Georgia, China, the CIS, Middle East and Europe countries, the on a single platform, giving them the opportunity to present their products with dignity and as efficiently as possible. The exclusivity of regional trade-industrial exhibition forum "ARMENIA EXPO" in its thematic construction is that it is covering almost all industries. While combining individual exposure to the largest industrial exhibition in Armenia, "ARMENIA EXPO" makes it possible to more fully explore and get the necessary information about all existing firms, organizations and brands that exist not only in Armenia, but also in the whole region, to find a profitable business partner or a foreign investor and contributes to maintaining a successful marketing. Subject: inquiry about your products
TextBody: -- Dear Sir, Greetings from Ghana. I am Ayoni Ayew Ayoni from Ayew Unique Supply Company Limited. I am an importer and business consultant based in Accra, Ghana. I also represent manufacturers and suppliers who wish to have their brands in Ghana. I would like to send you a request for quote. Please send me a brochure, product catalogue and price details of your products. Also inform me your nearest sales office to Ghana.

Subject: Infos Flocons Pomme de Terre//Agristo
TextBody: Bonjour Zahïa , Merci pour votre retour. Comme dans le mail je travaille sur le réseau Kosher en France et Europe. Concernant la certification si vous avez c est très bien ou sinon je peux fournir mes rabbins dans ce cas c est moi qui paie les frais de certification. Pour les volumes c est dans le mail envoyé et confirme moi si tu as aussi gamme flocons de pomme de terre pour retails. Prévoir entre 2 et 3 production par an (33 palettes)par production. En attente de ton retour et appelle moi pour échanger. Sincèrement, Bests

Subject: Fwd: SCG // Request on French fries to Saudi
TextBody: Dear Zahïa How are you? Thanks a lot for your reply Please see attached the replies on your question I have sent already in 2022. I am Ms Saada Daud., 21 years old and I am from Cote d'Ivoire,I am the only child of late Prof Michel Daud who was murdered by REBELS in Cote D'Ivoire Before the death of my late father he had a money a deposited with a Bank in Abidjan Cote D'Ivoire that contains the sum of ($1,500,000.00) One Million Five Hundred Thousand United States Dollars Please, I need your assistance to enable the Bank to transfer the money to your country for the investments purpose also in order to be my guardian, I am willing to offer you reasonable percentage from the total money as compensation for your effort Your Sincerely Ms Saada Daud

Subject: Gamma Export - Agristo (Belgium frozen potatoes)
TextBody: Good morning Zahïa, Thanks a lot for your email. I will submit this information to our product specialist in Cuba and will be back to you as soon as possible. In order to offer your products in Cuba, it is required presenting them before the competent authority for a sanitary registration. The following informtion will be needed: 1. Sanitary/health certificate of the factory 2. Technical sheets per prodcut reference, covering logistic information, useful life and EAN codes. 3. Radioactivity certificate per product. In case you do not have it, we might proceed with it in Cuba. 4. Samples. Once we have selected the references to work with, we will ask you for some samples.

Subject: Elevate Your Business in Japan! Here is the Key First Step
TextBody: Exhibiting Information Request If you are having trouble reading this email, read the online version<https://app.campaign.rxjapan.jp/e/es?s=12511217&e=85422&elqTrackId=49bd961a5a0d4c9aab8b5d9dc0d7e78f&elq=caddff263dfe496fac2ca6d30750d433&elqaid=59029&elqat=1>. Hello! We are LIFESTYLE Week Osaka [September] show management. We would like to extend an invitation to participate in our upcoming exhibition. We believe this event will be instrumental in expanding your sales channels in western Japan. We kindly request your consideration. For requesting the detail of LIFESTYLE Week Osaka, please register in the below URL. Exhibiting Information Request ►<https://app.campaign.rxjapan.jp/e/er?utm_campaign=exprom_en_0620&utm_medium=email&utm_source=Eloqua&querytoken=a09KqKy%2FTjRZP6LrCFWuk4IRpRkOTyn9fxsU0BwCu0BRCzIBHrK6sxB8GKCtmHWW5USFMfv%2B%2BKLUo%2BWGtIYKSA%3D%3D&s=12511217&lid=16401&elqTrackId=BA5122065386B4038C229E788441AF5A&elq=caddff263dfe496fac2ca6d30750d433&elqaid=59029&elqat=1> <Highlights of the September Kansai Exhibition>> ◆ Approximately 400 companies will participate in the exhibition, expecting 15,000 visitors. ◆ A chance for sales expansion in response to increased demand due to the Expo: The Osaka Expo, scheduled to be held from April to October 2025, is projected to attract a total of 28.2 million visitors, including 3.5 million inbound visitors from overseas. ◆ Retailers, wholesalers, and managers from major distributors in western Japan are expected to attend. With 90% of visitors being different from those at the Tokyo exhibition, this event provides an excellent opportunity for sales expansion focused on western Japan. If you are interested in exhibiting, please feel free to contact us. We eagerly await your inquiry. LIFESTYLE Week Osaka Dates: September 27th (Wednesday) to September 29th (Friday), 2023 Venue: Intex Osaka ◆ Applicable Product Categories ◆ • Variety goods • Beauty/health products • Outdoor goods • Fashion accessories • Sustainable goods • Food gifts • Tableware/kitchen goods • Baby products ...and more ◆ Target Audience ◆ • General merchandise stores • Department stores/supermarkets • Wholesalers/export-import businesses • Select shops • Online retail/e-commerce stores • Interior design shops • Apparel stores • Lifestyle shops ...and more We look forward to your participation. Sincerely, Yugo Matsuoka For more information, please contact:​ Lifestyle Week Tokyo Show Management Organiser: RX Japan Ltd.

Subject: ANUGA 2023-we build your stand
TextBody: Dear Sir or Madame, It is Klaudia Jon out here, let me introduce the company I work for. WeSee Construction Trade Fair Coopering and Event Partner We are Polish family company, exhibition cooperant and event partner. Our employees carry out projects with internal and external fairs. Now we are ready to support and to cooperate with new customers. We are able to organize everything from the project, services reservation and ordering to construction of course and disassembly. We will be very pleased if we could support you with stand construction at ANUGA 2023, or other trades in Europe you plan to participate. Please forward this e-mail to right person if you are not the right one [cid:_Foxmail.1@772ea24f-c953-adf1-d88e-5352bb758cd4] I invite you for a walk around the stand we built: https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=uQuixYAfkhp&vrcoll=1&qs=1 [cid:_Foxmail.1@cff0cec0-1580-f0dd-e892-fd390d6557c6] [Obraz zawierający wewnątrz, podłoże, budynek, sufit Opis wygenerowany automatycznie] [cid:_Foxmail.1@3dcd81f1-1309-8ee1-195d-ec56f768450c] [Obraz zawierający budynek, wewnątrz, sufit, pociąg Opis wygenerowany automatycznie] [Obraz zawierający wewnątrz, stół Opis wygenerowany automatycznie] [cid:_Foxmail.1@49e40a04-1286-a247-d55b-886d4371e876] Z pozdrowieniem /

Subject: Cooperation
TextBody: Dear Zahiia, Sorry for long pause. Can you please give prices for French fries for food service (2.5kg) also with logistic data- psc per box, boxes per pallet. I need to calculate logistic. For this type of product min order per month 10000kg

Subject: informatie
TextBody: Goedemiddag Ik ben op zoek naar friet. Ik wil 3 tot 5 containers per week afnemen. Zou u mij kunnen informeren over welke soorten friet jullie hebben, in welke verpakkingen ( is er een mogelijkheid voor private label), welke hoeveelheden en natuurlijk de prijs. Subject: product request
TextBody: Good evening Zahia Al-Salihi We are Al-Tarweqa Al-Muttahidah Trading Est Foodstuff Import and Marketing Corporation Commercial registration number / 4032258399 Tax number / 305001123300003 Address / Kingdom of Saudi Arabia - Taif Thank you for your interest in our message Company profile/ We are a Saudi institution and we work in importing and marketing foodstuffs. We want to work with you in (half-fried potatoes or frozen potatoes). purchase plan We are initially importing 100 tons of potatoes size 10 per month from your company and we have a plan to increase the quantity over time. distribution plan We have wholesalers such as the Fuel Trading Company, a specialized marketing and distribution company based in Jeddah We have distribution cars for the organization and storage refrigerators at the required 18 degrees Have you already purchased frozen (potato) products? What is your experience in this field? We have not bought potatoes before, and there are no contracts with any company yet, and you are the first company we deal with What volumes of fries per SKU do you do annually? We want size 10, which is desirable in the Saudi market after studying the market We are initially targeting the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, and we have an expansion plan in the future Do you have your own distribution channel or partners? What about warehouses? Yes, we have coordination with warehouses, cars, and delegates to distribute to restaurants, buffets, shawarma shops, and fast food restaurants. What is your market strategy? Who are your customers? We target restaurants, buffets, shawarma shops, and broasted restaurants in particular. We have wholesalers and supermarkets. Please see attached product specifications. Our terms in the product/ 1- The product should be crispy and not absorb oil 2- It should not have a percentage of fracture 3- It should not be green in colour questions / 1- How much is your company's production capacity? 2-Do you accept packaging with our brand name? 3- Is the shipment FOB or CIF? 4-How much is the price per ton cif? 5- Do you accept visits to your company? Thank you With Regards Ali Ahmed ________________________________ من: Agristo Sales <sales@agristo.com> ‏‏تم الإرسال: 08/ذو الحجة/1444 10:02 ص إلى: muasasat.altarwiqat@hotmail.com <muasasat.altarwiqat@hotmail.com> ‏‏الموضوع: RE: Product request [ thread::0ofv1UkoFW2sTxYCGyMv13Q:: ] Dear Ali, Thank you for your email and your interest in our company. To evaluate your request, we want to get a better picture of your company. Could you inform us and give some detailed information regarding: * Do you already purchase frozen (potato) products? Subject: budget potato and onion ring , 100% prepayment
TextBody: Dear Daniela, Thank you for your email and your interest in our company. At Agristo we have decided to focus on working directly with end buyers, as we believe this will provide the best value to our customers and ultimately drive the success of our business. Unfortunately, this means that we will not be able to work with intermediaries such as yourself. The reason behind this decision is that by working directly with the end buyers we can have a better understanding of the market trends and have more control over the prices and terms of the transactions. This will also allow us to have a direct relationship with our customers which we believe will be beneficial for both parties. We would like to thank you for your interest in working with us and hope that you understand our decision.

Subject: Join MIFB's Sustainability Journey
TextBody: The first F&B show to measure and compost food waste If you are not able to see this mail, click here<https://arse1.r.ag.d.sendibm3.com/mk/mr/sh/1t6AVsd2XFnIGNTuQCY3EZXajgZ9JG/vSbr9hNXcJfQ> [https://arse1.r.ag.d.sendibm3.com/mk/op/qVBmLnHBcx98QYVm9WVDq1xoAos1oGYhPfI1iuhaPuWR4BWspf9YExpieHpYjxs_n2bfKld1VAPfkwIbPD6J7C7mDyfMfxgTTRixZv_LsLuX1Fz5YvYV7sgHJjRP-vcRDdyBMb81QkJwdqdN] [cid:93808.7873971609437] MIFB is the first F&B trade show in Malaysia to measure and address food waste generated at the event. In partnership with Kuala Lumpur Convention Centre, exhibitors’ and visitors’ food waste generated during the event will be collected, weighed, identified and composted for crop fertiliser, benefiting and supporting the orang asli (indigenous) communities in Malaysia. [cid:55300.6729805673442] We invite you to join our movement to reduce food waste and take sustainable actions through individual efforts, however big or small they may be. Subject: RFQ from Poland
TextBody: Wysłano z mojego urządzenia Galaxy Good Morning, I represent a group of Polish companies from HORECA sector looking to buy packed frozen fries in packs of 1-3 kgs (or other - anything will be considered). In Poland we only have 3 factories, but they work at full speed and aren't interested to acquire new customers. Our needs are 10 to 20 000 kg a month so demand is considerably high. We plan single - consolidated orders (as above) since we have logistics partner to help reconsolidate. Transport on our side. Please be so kind to send availibility and net prices by the end of week. We have untill end of June to find supplier. Thank you very much in advance Should you have questions and/ or concerns - do not hesitate to contact me. Regards Tytus Ułanowski Business Development Manager +48 535 222 625

Subject: Automation for Lean Manufacturing: Optimizing Efficiency and Waste Reduction
TextBody: In this email, you will learn more about automation and how to optimize efficiency and waste reduction. ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ [https://content.app-us1.com/cdn-cgi/image/dpr=2,fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,width=650/WYkQG/2021/07/16/e3fd5507-7b71-4423-9b63-56ab23d2de91.png?r=244221705] Hello! Manufacturers are always looking for ways to increase productivity, cut waste, and strengthen their competitive advantage in their aim of excellence in operation. The use of automation in lean manufacturing practices is an effective tool for achieving those goals. Manufacturing can be revolutionized by automation, which also reduces waste, enhances process efficiency, and ultimately promote operational excellence. Waste is a primary concern for lean manufacturing, as it hinders productivity and increases costs. Automation offers a multitude of ways to eliminate waste in manufacturing processes: * Overproduction - Products are made in excess of what is needed, which results in higher inventory and storage expenses. Automation technology can help businesses optimize production based on real-time demand information. * Waiting - In the manufacturing industry, waiting time is an important contributor of waste. It happens when supplies, machinery, or personnel are not in use, which causes holdups and inefficiencies. * Processing - automation is essential for raising the effectiveness and quality of processes. Businesses can increase manufacturing precision, consistency, and speed by automating repetitive processes. Want to learn more about the solutions? TextBody: Unite in Supporting Local Talent! Subject: Introductie - aanvraag
TextBody: Beste Pedro, Ik heb je aanvraag intern besproken en na zorgvuldige overweging hebben we geconstateerd dat er mogelijk verschillen zijn tussen jouw strategie en die van Agristo. Op basis hiervan is het voor ons op dit moment niet haalbaar om de samenwerking voort te zetten. We willen je bedanken voor je interesse om met ons samen te werken en hopen dat je begrip hebt voor onze beslissing. We wensen je het allerbeste toe in al je toekomstige zakelijke plannen. Vriendelijke groeten, Zahïa Salhi --------------- Original Message --------------- From: Pedro Augusto [paugusto@ngm-international.com] Sent: 29/06/2023 12:05 To: sales@agristo.com Subject: Introductie - aanvraag Beste Heer en of Mevrouw, Mijn naam is Pedro Augusto, ik ben de Directeur van NGM International B.V. NGM International is een in Rotterdam gevestigd familiebedrijf die zich sinds haar oprichting in 1982 bezighoudt met de internationale promotie en distributie van levensmiddelen, alles onder eigen merken. Voor onze klant in Israël – één van de belangrijkste spelers in de lokale food service – zijn wij momenteel op zoek naar een producent van diepgevroren frites, welke overigens kosher gecertificeerd moeten zijn. Graag zouden wij vernemen of uw bedrijf mogelijk interesse zou hebben om naar deze specifieke aanvraag te kijken. Bij voorbaat onze dank voor uw aandacht en opvolging. The government’s initiatives and investments to improve the tourism landscape is expected to drive the hospitality sector’s development. Subject: Anuga 2023 – Invitation to the high-level UNIDO expert event: „A World without Hunger is possible“
TextBody: Open in browser<https://smc-seb.s4hana.ondemand.com/eu/elastic-access/sap/seb/?_L54AD1F204_=c2NlbmFyaW89U0VCJnRlbmFudD1teTMwMDI1Ny5zNGhhbmEub25kZW1hbmQuY29tJkNhbXBhaWduT3V0Ym91bmQ9J0IxMTBBODk3ODE2MDY5MzhGRjMwNUFFNjA3MzEyQTQxMDg0N0NBMkYnJkxpbmtUcmFja2luZ0lzRGlzYWJsZWQ9ZmFsc2U&_K13_=252&_K14_=196fe6630d3dbff052d25794257a5035d955652dd58fea174ad80517cc3c0900> [ANUGA23]<https://smc-link.s4hana.ondemand.com/eu/data-buffer/sap/public/cuan/link/100/B110A89781606938FF305AE607312A410847CA2F?_V_=2&_K11_=2FF5D898469121BD6C71597CDF74A891DA12EA0C&_L54AD1F204_=c2NlbmFyaW89TUxDUEcmdGVuYW50PW15MzAwMjU3LnM0aGFuYS5vbmRlbWFuZC5jb20mdGFyZ2V0PWh0dHBzOi8vd3d3LmFudWdhLmNvbS8%2Fc2FwLW91dGJvdW5kLWlkPUIxMTBBODk3ODE2MDY5MzhGRjMwNUFFNjA3MzEyQTQxMDg0N0NBMkYmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1TQVBIeWJyaXMmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249MTU3ODEmdXRtX3Rlcm09MDAyNV8yM19BV19OTDQ2ZV9Vbmlkb19fX0FOVUdBJnV0bV9jb250ZW50PUVO&_K13_=471&_K14_=9419a920cdafb2459bd422dc81164c4b126567ca6d0c9b7937eef23294d279ce> Dear Ms. Wallays, According to UN estimates, 800 million people worldwide are not adequately nourished or go hungry. This makes worldwide hunger the greatest global health risk, and the challenges will continue to increase in times of climate change and a growing world population. On Anuga Saturday, the UNIDO<https://smc-link.s4hana.ondemand.com/eu/data-buffer/sap/public/cuan/link/100/B110A89781606938FF305AE607312A410847CA2F?_V_=2&_K11_=0B0EBCC1F2D1A17E3A5352DEF83523E968F6A5BB&_L54AD1F204_=c2NlbmFyaW89TUxDUEcmdGVuYW50PW15MzAwMjU3LnM0aGFuYS5vbmRlbWFuZC5jb20mdGFyZ2V0PWh0dHBzOi8vd3d3LnVuaWRvLm9yZy8%2FdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1TQVBIeWJyaXMmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249MTU3ODEmdXRtX3Rlcm09MDAyNV8yM19BV19OTDQ2ZV9Vbmlkb19fX1VOSURPJnV0bV9jb250ZW50PUVO&_K13_=471&_K14_=f0a39c264952e59a60abd590549df86b8e322db4ed13ac04eb6128cd2bec29f7> (United Nations Industrial Development Organizations) will present options for action at the high-level expert event "A World Without Hunger is Possible"<https://smc-link.s4hana.ondemand.com/eu/data-buffer/sap/public/cuan/link/100/B110A89781606938FF305AE607312A410847CA2F?_V_=2&_K11_=3939A184CDB357465E45816BB2D2704D5E6B86C5&_L54AD1F204_=c2NlbmFyaW89TUxDUEcmdGVuYW50PW15MzAwMjU3LnM0aGFuYS5vbmRlbWFuZC5jb20mdGFyZ2V0PWh0dHBzOi8vd3d3LmFudWdhLmNvbS9ldmVudHMvY29uZ3Jlc3Nlcy91bmlkb19lbi8%2FdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1TQVBIeWJyaXMmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249MTU3ODEmdXRtX3Rlcm09MDAyNV8yM19BV19OTDQ2ZV9Vbmlkb19fX0FudWdhJTIwVU5JRE8lMjBDb25mZXJlbmNlJnV0bV9jb250ZW50PUVO&_K13_=471&_K14_=2627afee74e505921f1435917fdf5c3ceedbba51933bdbed70ca86bc21710fcf>. Subject: Proposal for Procurement of USDA Approved Frozen French Fries for US Schools
TextBody: Dear Agristo, I hope this message finds you well. My name is El Khattary and I represent Mana Food Sales, a modern sales and marketing agency headquartered in Austin, Texas (https://manafoodsales.com/about/). I am writing to inquire about the possibility of purchasing approximately 2,267 metric tons (or 5 million lbs) of frozen French fries from Agristo. We are aware that Agristo is a highly respected manufacturer of frozen pre-fried French fries and potato specialties, operating multiple production plants across Belgium and the Netherlands. Our intention is to serve these fries in K-12 schools across the United States. In light of this, it is essential that the products meet USDA standards for school meals. In particular, the USDA has several requirements that are relevant for fries served in school meals: - No added sugars - Grain-based foods (like fries made from potatoes) should be at least 80% whole grain-rich; the remaining items must be enriched. - Sodium content should meet specific targets set by the USDA, with incremental reductions planned for future school years. We are therefore particularly interested in whether Agristo's products can meet these specifications, as well as any other information you can provide about the nutrition content of your fries. We look forward to potentially working with Agristo and appreciate your consideration of this proposal. Please feel free to reach out if you need any further information from us. Thank you for your time.

Subject: WI-FI Access: Anuga 2023, Messe Cologne
TextBody: Dear Exhibitor, FAIREXPO would like to offer your company a reliable and cost-efficient solution for the Internet access during the Anuga show in Cologne from 7 - 11 October 2023. We offer a flexible range of Internet packages that allow you to connect to the Internet up to 10 or 30 devices (depending on the chosen router model) creating a fast, reliable and secure network at your exhibition booth. Our trade show Internet services include: ■ Mobile in-booth network solutions ■ Secure VPN capabilities ■ High-density reliable wireless service ■ Full-time monitoring through our Network Operations Center ■ On-site support ■ Flexible service offerings & data top ups Following types of the wi-fi connection and data packages are available and can be booked with us for your next trade show: * prices refer to the whole show period and are not daily rates. STANDARD WI-FI LTE BUSINESS PRO SMART 20 GB Data Plan - € 220,00 ULTRA 25 GB Data Plan - € 260,00 PREMIUM 30 GB Data Plan - € 299,00 BRONZE 30 GB Data Plan - € 330,00 SILVER 40 GB Data Plan - € 399,00 GOLD 50 GB Data Plan - € 450,00 Delivery & pickup: the Wi-Fi router will be installed at your stand on the 6th October (2:00 pm - 5:00 p.m.) and collected on the 11th October (5:00 - 6:00 p.m.). Deposit: a refundable security deposit of 50,00 Euro will be charged on the delivery day and returned on the day of the router pickup. Booking: to sign up for the service or for more information, please send us an email or use the attached order form. Other types of technical equipment we provide: digital displays, cell phone & tablet charging stations, power tables, sanitizing kiosks etc.

Rendez-vous du 22 au 24 octobre à Paris Villepinte. [https://natexpo.com/exposer/recevez-demande-dadmission/]<https://link.event.spas-expo.com/m/ml/200253/508486/i9-nrB9zC2pjZF2XkwI64Q==/8fkXftKdGk6nNuJAuPQ1VdVuY4HI43CbCOd2-Z0LxE4=/AwhOYXRleHBvXzIwMjNfcHJvc3BlY3Rpb24gOCBGUiBFTg==> Certes, participer au salon, c'est un budget, MAIS cette année, pour la première fois, nous vous proposons un paiement échelonné. Certes, participer au salon c'est une sacrée organisation, MAIS c'est avant tout faire le choix de bénéficier d'un outil commercial qui va vous permettre de développer des contacts ciblés. Certes, la conjoncture est compliquée, MAIS des signaux positifs apparaissent et c'est maintenant qu'il faut les saisir. Subject: COMPENATIONS FROM FEDERAL GOVERNMENT OF NIGERIA IN AFFILIATION WITH IMF AND WORLD BANK.
TextBody: Good day A Power of Attorney was forwarded to our office this morning by a gentle man, who is a British national with the name MR NICKOLA WARD.This gentlemen claimed to be your representative, and this power of attorney stated that you are dead. He brought an account to replace your information*s in other to claim your fund of $4.5 Million US which it is right now lying DORMANT and UNCLAIMED, below is the new Bank name and information he submitted..... NatWest Bank address...... Premier place devonshire square London ECDM 4*B Swift code...... 560045 Router Number.... IBAN GB85 NWBK 56004535626887 Acct Name....... NICKOLA WARD Acct Number.......35626887Bank name..... Nat. West Bank address...... Premier place devonshire square London ECDM 4*B Swift code...... 560045 Router Number.... IBAN GB85 NWBK 56004535626887 Acct Name....... NICKOLA WARD Acct Number.......35626887 Be further informed that this power of attorney also stated that you suffered and died of a cancer. You are therefore given 24hrs to confirm the truth in this information, If you are still alive, You are to contact us back immediately because we work 24 hours just to ensure that we monitor all the activities going on in regards to the transfer of beneficiaries inheritance and contract payment. Please you are hereby advice to reconfirm the below information to this honorable office for confirmation to help us serve you better the International Monetary Fund (IMF want this. Your Full Name................. Your Country Address........... Your Home Address.............. Occupation..................... Telephone Or Cell Phone.............. A Copy Of Your ID............... The National Central Bureau of Interpol enhanced by the United Nations and Federal Bureau of Investigation have successfully passed a mandate to the new president of Nigeria his Excellency President Bola Ahmed Tinubu to boost the exercise of clearing all foreign debts owed to Foreigners and Compensate all that have lost their hard earned money to the Nigeria Fraudsters. UNITED NATIONS COMPENSATION IN CONJUNCTION WITH FEDERAL GOVERNMENT OF NIGERIA IN AFFILIATION WITH WORLD BANK. This is your File Reference (RE-1077-V) and you are free to get back to me asap. Subject: Possible partnership
TextBody: Good morning, I trust this email finds you well. My name is Vince, I'm responsible for the purchasing of Farm Meat Market. Colleagues of mine had visited your exhibition at Anuga 2021. At that time, our company was mainly a meat importer and distributor. I did a bit of research myself about your company and belief that there are opportunities for both of us. Can we start by having a look at your range of potato products and the different packaging? For your perusal, kindly find our company's information sheet. Should you need more information, please do not hesitate to ask.

Subject: Transform Your Anuga Trade Show Booth with Cutting-Edge Media Equipment Rentals
TextBody: Rental Price List 2023 [Logo] [Rental Range] ________________________________ Dear Anuga Exhibitor, Thank you for considering RS Media Solutions as your partner for media equipment rentals at your upcoming trade show. We are excited to introduce you to our range of specialized media equipment designed to help you create an impactful booth that captures the attention of attendees. We kindly request that you forward this email to the person in charge of the exhibition planning, ensuring they have access to all the relevant information. Here are the key reasons why RS Media Solutions can make a significant difference for your trade show experience: 1. Expertise and Specialization: With our extensive experience in the field, we understand the unique requirements and challenges faced by exhibitors like you. Our expertise allows us to provide you with the most suitable and technologically advanced equipment, ensuring your booth creates a lasting impact. 2. Wide Range of Options: We offer a diverse selection of media equipment options to customize your booth experience. From LED walls to display splits and single signage displays, we have the perfect solution to match your specific needs, booth size, and budget. 3. Quality and Reliability: Our commitment to delivering exceptional results means we only offer high-quality, meticulously maintained equipment. You can rely on our products without concerns about technical issues or equipment failures during the event. Our inventory consists of professional-grade equipment specifically designed for rental and exhibition usage, ensuring optimal performance and durability. We do not provide equipment intended for home use, guaranteeing that you have access to reliable and industry-standard media solutions for your trade show booth. 4. Customization and Flexibility: We understand that your booth should reflect your brand identity and design preferences. That's why we provide tailored customization options to align the media equipment with your unique requirements. We will collaborate closely with you to adjust size, resolution, or content displayed on the screens, ensuring your booth stands out and effectively communicates your message. 5. Professional Support: Our dedicated support team is available to provide on-site assistance throughout the event. We are experienced in installation, troubleshooting, and content management, allowing you to focus on your core objectives during the trade show. 6. Cost-Effective Solution: We offer competitive pricing for our media equipment rentals. Our transparent pricing structure and flexible rental packages empower you to choose a solution that aligns with your budget without compromising the visual impact and effectiveness of your booth. For our current offers and detailed pricing information, please visit [insert website]. 7. Cost Considerations: Renting directly from the exhibition organizer or stand builder may result in higher costs due to limited competition and potential markup. RS Media Solutions offers competitive pricing for our rentals, along with transparent pricing structures and flexible rental packages. This enables you to choose a cost-effective solution that fits within your budget without compromising the quality or effectiveness of your booth. We highly recommend considering RS Media Solutions as your preferred partner for media equipment rentals. Our combination of expertise, a wide range of options, quality, customization, professional support, and cost-effectiveness makes us the ideal choice for exhibitors like you. To provide you with a glimpse of our current rental offers, we have included an excerpt below this email.

Subject: Last call to exhibit at FHO, the largest international trade show for the food and hospitality industry in Oman!
TextBody: If you are having trouble reading this email, read the online version.<https://info.foodandhospitalityoman.com/c/110NsOj2Zoi8S8un2H8JduSxKl> [FHO Header] <https://info.foodandhospitalityoman.com/c/110NtwbPN8kXmMgz9cq34tDiJU> Dear Industry Colleague, Food and Hospitality Oman (FHO)<https://info.foodandhospitalityoman.com/c/110Nue4CASnLRq2LfHHmVso3Jt> trade show is just around the corner! With only 10 weeks to go, we wanted to ensure that you are aware of this incredible opportunity to showcase your products and services to a global audience. [Book your Stand] <https://info.foodandhospitalityoman.com/c/110NuVXpoCqAm3OXmcYGMr8OJ2> FHO<https://info.foodandhospitalityoman.com/c/110NvDQccmtoQHB9sIg0DpTzIB> taking place between 18 – 20 September, has established itself as the largest international trade show for the food and hospitality industry in Oman. It serves as a platform for exhibitors from around the world to connect with key decision-makers, industry experts, and potential business partners. FHO<https://info.foodandhospitalityoman.com/c/110NwlIZ06wdllnlzdxkuoEkIa> is supported by the esteemed Ministry of Agriculture, Fisheries Wealth and Water Resources. This support reflects the significance of the event and the valuable opportunities it presents to promote business development and innovation in the food and hospitality sectors. Additionally, FHO<https://info.foodandhospitalityoman.com/c/110NxLuyBABQkCVJMe5Ycm9QHi> has garnered the support of renowned industry professionals and organizations, further validating its position as a premier trade show in Oman. These organizations include: Abu Dhabi Department of Economic Development, Trade Development Authority of Pakistan and PHD Chamber of Commerce of India and Sri Lankan Export Development Board. Subject: Hello Good Day,
TextBody: Compliments, I am Nicolas Lemue, a Financial Consultant from France however resident in London, United Kingdom. I want to partner with you on a transaction worth $80M USD. I had a client who unfortunately died of COVID-19 complications from 2020. I want you to receive this money as a representative for of my late client. He died intestate together with his nominated next of kin unfortunately. I shall provide to you all appropriate legal documents that will present you as a legal representative and entitlement to these assets/estate. Part of this estate is in AU METAL (120kg). When you reply, we shall discuss a whole lot of issues including disbursement modalities and of course any questions you will have regarding to the process. If your response is yes, kindly send a contact number where I could reach you in all privacy.

Subject: Fairfilm Anuga Cologne 2023
TextBody: Dear AGRISTO -Team, We are a production company for audiovisual media, situated in Wuppertal, with over 10 years of experience in the fields of culture and events. We would like to produce an individual short film (20-60 sec.) for you, which will give the viewer a first impression of your products and services at the Anuga Cologne 2023, perfectly suited for the presentation on your online- and social-media channels. In addition to the professional video- and audio recordings, we are offering a bundle package with 10 photographs for a small surcharge. Of course, we can provide you with extra photos. The flat-rate fee is 10 EUR per photo (plus VAT). If you accept the offer, our team will record footage of your booth as well as footage containing your product highlights and combine it in a short video clip. The production of the short film without the photographs will be 350 EUR (plus VAT). The bundle, including the recording of audio and video material, data management, postproduction and the distribution of the final film and photographs, amounts to 450 EUR (plus VAT). We also offer professional voice recordings for your fair trade video for an additional 80 EUR (plus VAT). In order to give you an idea of what your film could look like, we would like to show you three short films that we have produced recently. At the FIBO 2022, we produced an Instagram-clip about innovative training machines for Vitruvian Product Pty LTD. https://vimeo.com/697550320/755fff9ecf At the BioWest 2022 we produced a short promotion video for the food manufacturer Teutoburger Ölmühle GmbH. https://vimeo.com/698585130/0f7c122e5b In order to give you an insight into our projects outside of fair trades, here’s a teaser we produced for the shoe brand Blundstone. https://vimeo.com/716414409/a63ffc6356 As we want to give you a full impression of our field of production, we included this short clip that we produced for the opening ceremony 2022 of the Lehmbruck Museum. https://vimeo.com/692343018/18cc1329a2 We are looking forward to hearing from you! Yours Sincerely Mari Gasparov Exhibition Team Siegersbusch [https://www.siegersbusch.de/logoSignatur.png] [„facebook“] [„instagram“] SIEGERSBUSCH FILM, JEUCKENS/WINDUS GBR, FRIEDRICH-EBERT-STR.143E, 42117 WUPPERTAL TELEFON: 0202 42 99 08 78 TELEFAX: 0202 716 740 18 WWW.SIEGERSBUSCH.DE

Subject: BergHOFF = duurzaam| durable
TextBody: Bekijk dit bericht in je browser<https://cdn.flxml.eu/r-198b9480846b609ca4f846ecb4b03b29fb8648348d291929> [https://cdn.flxml.eu/dyn/tpl_attributes/user_images/user_1219_images/duurzaam_banner.jpg?v=1689342025559] <https://cdn.flxml.eu/lt-2186474014-198b9480846b609ca4f846ecb4b03b29fb8648348d291929> Kies voor duurzame en betekenisvolle personeels-/relatiegeschenken met BergHOFF Als bedrijf dat toegewijd is aan duurzaam ondernemen, biedt BergHOFF heel wat mogelijkheden. BergHOFF biedt niet alleen hoogwaardige producten, maar heeft ook ook een sterke focus op het bevorderen van mens en natuur. Bij BergHOFF geloven we dat duurzaamheid meer is dan alleen een trend; het is een integraal onderdeel van onze bedrijfsvoering. Waarom kiezen voor BergHOFF? BergHOFF Onderneemt actie voor verduurzaming op het vlak van onder meer verpakking & verzending, energieverbruik, klimaatneutraliteit en welzijn op het werk. [https://cdn.flxml.eu/dyn/tpl_attributes/user_images/user_1219_images/verpakking.jpg?v=1689342600005] BergHOFF lanceert een hele reeks van nieuwe producten, geproduceerd met gerecycleerde materialen. [https://cdn.flxml.eu/dyn/tpl_attributes/user_images/user_1219_images/web_3950420-441_014.jpg?v=1689342757699] BergHOFF bouwt met gelijkgestemde partners en klanten aan een duurzame kook- en keukenwereld en engageren ze zich voor uiteenlopende lidmaatschappen en duurzaamheidscharters. Lees meer https://berghoff-belgium.be/pages/duurzaamheidsstrategie [https://cdn.flxml.eu/dyn/tpl_attributes/user_images/user_1219_images/duurzaamboom.jpg?v=1689342941916] Wie is BergHOFF BergHOFF is een merk van Belgische bodem gespecialiseerd in alles wat met koken te maken heeft. Kies je voor een samenwerking met ons dan krijg je gegarandeerd een betrouwbare partner met bijna 30 jaar ervaring in kook – en keukengerei. Met deze producten en vanuit een ecologisch, sociaal én financieel gezond beleid kiest BergHOFF Belgium krachtig voor klimaatneutraliteit. Het doel? Samen met gelijkgestemde partners bouwen aan de duurzame kook- en keukenwereld van morgen. Bij ons kan je terecht voor allerlei verschillende toepassingen gaande van relatiegeschenken, kerstpakketten, incentives, spaaracties, personalisatie van producten, uniek samengestelde boxen en nog veel meer. Bovendien is keukengerei een perfecte informatiedrager, het wordt dagelijks gebruikt! Graveren, bedrukken, brandmerken, herverpakken ...alles is mogelijk! Met thema, budget, aantallen,...kunnen wij aan de slag! We werken graag een voorstel op maat uit. Klaar voor een samenwerking? Bekijk dan wat we voor je kunnen betekenen via onderstaande knop.

Subject: Transportation services and partnership offer.
TextBody: Hello, I am Sarunas from Freightia logistics company. I am responsible for sales. We are logistics company based which specializes in high quality freight forwarding services by international routes. We are currently looking for co-operation and partnership possibilities with other companies. Services we are providing: * Full truck loads. General, mixed, neutral and consolidated freights. Shipping with tent/curtain-sider trailers (loading from side/back). Capacity of trailer: up to 24 tons and 33 EUR. pallets. * Temperature controlled loads. Meat, fish, vegetables, fruits, dairy and other product freights which require temperature control. Shipping by refrigerated trailers which are certified by ATP (FRC) and iso-thermic (box) trailers (loading from the back), trailers with hooks. Capacity of trailers: up to 22-23 tons and 33 EUR. pallets. * Part truck loads. We are able to provide you optimal price offer for partial loads which consist from 1 to 20 pallets in accordance with type of pallets, approximate weight and measurements of the load. Our main transportation routes: UK, Benelux, Baltics, Poland, Scandinavia, Germany, France, Central Europe (Austria, Czech Republic, Slovakia, Hungary), Southern Europe (Italy, Spain) and other many countries. Our diversely skilled team are experienced in logistics, sales, marketing, management and providing customer service 24/7. We take pride in our wide chain of partners throughout Europe which let us to be more flexible & faster in the recent transport market. You can find more info at: www.freightia.lt<http://www.freightia.lt> If you are interested in any kind of cooperation, you are welcome to send your delivery directions, so that I would be able to provide a pricelist for you. Thank you for your time! [cid:image004.jpg@01D8818B.81E49C70]

Subject: Transport service
TextBody: Good morning I want offer you our transport service, we providing transport service all over europe. Mor-Trans Company with the head office in Gdynia is a modern company providing refrigerated transport services (wide temperature range -29/+27) as well as tarpaulin transport services with tarpaulin semi-trailers of standard, mega and tandem 120 m3 type. The company have been selling their products in all Europe since 1996. We offer transport directly from the warehouse of the ordering company to the consignee. We complete each transport order within a relatively short period of time. The exchange of pallets is available upon the client’s request. The commitment and passion we engage in our work allows to ensure high quality cooperation with our clients. We have a fleet of only new vehicles (Euro6): Refrigerated semi-trailers for 33 pallet space, maximum capacity of 22t Tarpaulin semi-trailers for 33 pallet space, maximum capacity 24t Combination of Tandem 120m3 type, maximum capacity In order to meet our client’s demands regarding a wide range of transport of both full truck loads and bulk load, we also offer forwarding services. We can offer a wide choice of carriers cooperating with our company, which ensures effective customer service regarding your transport needs in different directions with highly diverse fleet adjusted to your expectations. The management of Mor-Trans Company is highly qualified (appropriate professional education and Certificate of Professional Competency) and present a large amount of experience allowing to take proper decisions in difficult situations. The clients of Mor-Trans Company value the cooperation at a very high level making it easier to select a contractor for transportation projects. Professional service allows our clients to have good relations with their direct consignees which results with successful sale terms The market of refrigerated transport is highly demanding and challenging in respect of maintaining specific carriage conditions. It is for this reason that keeping the deadlines, proper training for drivers, hygienic conditions, regular disinfection and flexibility in operations are the top values in our business. Please visit our home page at www.mor-trans.pl<http://www.mor-trans.pl/> Pozdrawiam/

Subject: Mosselen by Piet Huysentruyt
TextBody: Bekijk dit bericht in je browser<https://cdn.flxml.eu/r-198b9480846b609ca4057e4db1fd7cc0082a63f395191a1f> [https://cdn.flxml.eu/dyn/tpl_attributes/user_images/user_1219_images/piet3.jpg?v=1689762027035] <https://cdn.flxml.eu/lt-2186519522-198b9480846b609ca4057e4db1fd7cc0082a63f395191a1f> Ontdek de veelzijdige mosselpot ontworpen door Piet Huysentruyt Het is weer die tijd van het jaar waar we allemaal naar hebben uitgekeken - het mosselseizoen is eindelijk hier! En dit keer hebben we iets echt speciaals voor jou: de veelzijdige mosselpot, ontworpen door niemand minder dan de beroemde chef-kok Piet Huysentruyt, in samenwerking met BergHOFF. Deze mosselpot is niet zomaar een gewone pot; het is een slimme 4-in-1 oplossing die je op meerdere manieren in de keuken van dienst kan zijn: 1) Mosselpot of kookpot: Natuurlijk is het belangrijkste kenmerk van deze pot dat het de ideale manier biedt om heerlijke mosselen te bereiden. Met zijn ruime formaat en hoogwaardige materialen zorgt deze pot ervoor dat jouw mosselen perfect gegaard worden, precies zoals je ze het liefste hebt. Inderdaad, de BergHOFF Mosselpot kan ook dienen als een gewone kookpot voor een breed scala aan gerechten. Met zijn hoogwaardige constructie en ruime formaat is het ideaal voor het blancheren van groenten zoals spinazie. Daarnaast kun je de pot gebruiken voor het bereiden van pasta, soepen, stoofschotels en nog veel meer. De veelzijdigheid van deze pot maakt het een onmisbaar hulpmiddel in jouw keuken. 2) Steamer: Het handige inzetstuk kan gebruikt worden als vergiet of kan ook worden gebruikt als een stoommandje. Hiermee kun je op een gezonde manier groenten, vis of andere lekkernijen stomen, terwijl je tegelijkertijd de authentieke smaak behoudt. 3) Bakvorm: Voeg het matje toe aan het inzetstuk, en je hebt een praktische bakvorm. Of je nu een heerlijke quiche, een smakelijke taart of een verrukkelijke ovenschotel wilt maken, deze mosselpot helpt je om creatief te zijn in de keuken. 4) Pan: Maar dat is nog niet alles! Het deksel van de is multifunctioneel en kan ook als pan worden gebruik. Via onderstaande link kan je naar zijn filmpje kijken hoe Piet het liefst zijn mosselen bereidt! Via de dealershop kan je het huidge assortiment van Piet by BergHOFF bestellen, de nieuwe reeks wordt verwacht in oktober.

Subject: Investment in the future of UK Mould Tool Manufacture
TextBody: [Plastic tooling Machine]<https://bit.ly/46UuV7M> Pentagon Tooling makes high-level investment to enhance mould tooling manufacture 2023 has seen Pentagon make significant investment into new CNC technology to deliver improved engineering capabilities within the Tooling Division. Between March and May this year the Group is delighted to have add Mikron VCE 600 Pro and two FROM E 600 to the plant list, purchased from long term supplier GF Machining Solutions. The new additions have the latest generator technology available and subsequently cut considerably quicker with a better final surface finish. With the larger working areas the engineering team area able to mount an increased quantity of work pieces at any one time and the automation now available reduces the man hours required for machining processes. Pentagon have truly raised the bar for improved efficiencies in UK Mould Tool manufacture, if you are looking to source a UK supplier for your next injection moulding project or you have existing mould tooling that requires service, repair or modification contact the engineering team on 01403264397 or sales@pentagonplastics.co.uk.<mailto:sales@pentagonplastics.co.uk> Learn more <https://bit.ly/46UuV7M> [Plastics Machine] Pentagon Plastics 2023 Unsubscribe <mailto:digimpe@unsub.industrynews4u.co.uk?subject=Unsubscribe%20from%20MPE>
