Subject: Workforce Support from Axialus
TextBody: Dear Sir/Madam I represent recruitment agency AXIALUS, we are based in Poland and I would like to find out if you have any urgent or future workforce needs and willing to use our support. Axialus hires temporary workers available for our clients demands. We take care of all administrative procedures, ranging from the whole recruitment process to organizing arrival of the employee at your premises. We closely cooperate with Van Havermaet, company which is our representative in Belgium and our legal advisor. All contributions and taxes are paid to Belgian official institutions, which allows us to meet all legal obligations and requirements. WHAT BENEFITS WILL YOU GET: o avoiding cost of job publications and adverts through various channels: industry websites, job boards etc. o reduced time spent on selection of applications and CVs, relevant skills verification, telephone and face to face interviews, o freed time spent on completing the hiring formalities, social declarations, employment contracts, medical examinations etc. o saved time spent on administrative follow-ups: payroll management, payslips issue, paid annual leaves, payroll tax, o flexibility in contract management: contract dates, covers, o avoiding costs generated by social litigation. OUR APPROVALS IN BELGIUM: We are proud holders of special approvals and certification issued by the Belgian authorities for three regions: - Brussels-Capital, approval n° 00570-406-20151211 - Wallonia, approval n° W.INT.1137 - Flanders, approval n° VG 2135/UC OUR SCOPE OF SERVICES INCLUDE: o full recruitment process, o coverage of costs of accommodation in Belgium, o medical examination in an occupational health care facility in Poland or Belgium, o submission of Limosa forms, o provision of A1 certificates, provision of the European Health Insurance Cards, o all HR and administrative (payroll) tasks, o payment of National Insurance contributions in Poland, o payment of mandatory contributions to OPOC or FSI, o supervision over the assignment performance for the contract duration. I would like to point out that Axialus operates in Belgium fully officially and legally. Before any employee is actually delegated to our client, we present full profile of the candidate for their acceptance. Everyone is issued with complete documentation required under Belgian and Polish law. Employee receives remuneration and bonuses in accordance with the collective bargaining principles (Joint Committee) client is affiliated to. What's more, each assignment is monitored by our logistics department. Each client has its own Account Manager. Please find form to complete attached. Filling in this form does not mean you agree to anything, it will help us understand your needs and allows us to asses our recruitment possibilities and prepare an offer. I really hope that our partnership proposal will be interested and you will consider our cooperation. Thank you for your time and please feel free to contact me if you have any more questions.

Subject: Registration closing soon - Expo Djibouti 25 - 28 October 2023
TextBody: Invitation to participate at EXPO DJIBOUTI 25- 28 OCT 2023, PALAIS DU PEUPLE - DJIBOUTI An Int'l Trade Expo on all kinds of consumer & industrial products Warm Greetings From African Trade! It is our great pleasure to invite your esteemed company to participate at the EXPO DJIBOUTI, an annual international trade exhibition for all kinds of consumer and industrial products. As an Exhibitor at the Expo Djibouti, you’ll have the opportunity to connect with hundreds of qualified Buyers & Distributors from all over DJIBOUTI, ETHIOPIA, SOMALIA, ERITREA & SUDAN eager to find new products and technology for their customers. The Expo Djibouti Exhibition is almost 91% booked and we have very limited stands available. With over 200 companies participating from 16 countries such as BELGIUM, CHINA, CYPRUS, GERMANY, INDIA, IRAN, JAPAN, KENYA, KOREA, LEBANON, MALAYSIA, OMAN, SAUDI ARABIA, THAILAND, UNITED ARAB EMIRATES, UNITED KINGDOM, ETC. WHY DJIBOUTI? Djibouti has continued to attract investors across multiple sectors, serving as a transit point between African, Middle Eastern and Asian markets. Indeed, as a natural gateway to the trade routes that cross the Red Sea and the Gulf, the country has positioned itself as a strategic partner for transport operations and energy trade. Transport links to neighbouring landlocked Ethiopia, in particular, have made Djibouti an integral part of international trade and commerce with the largest country and most dynamic market in the Horn of Africa. These favourable conditions have been compounded by a steady programme of infrastructure development. Public and private investment has given rise to new ports, roads and railway links, as well as critical energy and water assets to serve the country’s growing population. The result has been a fast and sustained expansion of GDP. OFFICIAL HOTEL: Sheraton Hotel Djibouti 5***** Les Acacias Hotel Djibouti 4***** SERVICE PROVIDED: We have arranged several participation options for our international participants which includes Modern shell stand with basic furniture, 5* & 4* Hotel Accommodation, Meet & Assist service on arrival, Visa, Media Coverage, Market & City Tours, Daily Transportation, Interpreter etc. Registration Closes on the 20th August Get in touch For information about our economic package which includes 9sqm Booth, Hotel, Transportation, etc on:- E-mail: info@african-trade.com Phone: +44 20 3432 4013 Become an Exhibitor African Trade 182-184 High Street North, East Ham, E6 2JA, London This email was sent to {{contact.EMAIL}} You've received it because you've subscribed to our newsletter. TextBody: Your chance to position your brand in front of key food and drink buyers [https://event.montgomerygroup.com/t/127IFJg7SQs4Ce.png]<https://event.montgomerygroup.com/c/1c5CA0xaton03a7kDbRVmMo> View this email online<https://event.montgomerygroup.com/q/1mbZ5QvfCyKKAbAUO2ID/wv> [https://event.montgomerygroup.com/i/amf_angus_montgomery/project_27/Email_Header/IFE_2024_email_header_3_.png?size=1200x0&w=BYJlPt1FgAsNwIcmtEw-y7VT0mEo] <https://event.montgomerygroup.com/c/1fBrk9k0KH5A6CfLuET9t3dD> Leverage the power of face-to-face at IFE 2024 IFE, International Food and Drink Event<https://event.montgomerygroup.com/c/1fBrGDrB05AzVegQmBsWEcjM>, brings together 27,000+ buyers and 1,500+ suppliers all under one roof to meet face-to-face and create high quality and effective business connections. This is your chance to position your brand in front of buyers from across the retail, foodservice, hospitality, wholesale, distribution, import and export sectors. Join us on 25-27 March 2024 at ExCeL London to uncover new business opportunities and differentiate your brand from your competitors. Secure your stand<https://event.montgomerygroup.com/c/1fBs37zbfu5zJQhVey2JPlpV> Top 3 benefits of doing business face-to-face at IFE [https://event.montgomerygroup.com/i/amf_angus_montgomery/project_27/Images/1.png?size=340x0&w=BrgGKEZH7xJrXnBN0ETkfRUiqhxM] Relationship Building: According to a Harvard Business Review study, face-to-face requests are 34 times more successful than those made via email. Meeting in person allows for stronger personal connections, so whether you’re meeting existing clients or potential clients at IFE, the event can help lead to increased trust and more fruitful business relationships. Where else would you meet 27,000 food and drink buyers all in one room to have face-to-face conversations with? [https://event.montgomerygroup.com/i/amf_angus_montgomery/project_27/Images/2.png?size=340x0&w=B24VqSOU1t4F0ein-bnjObetGHvI] Networking and Lead Generation: Trade shows like IFE provide valuable opportunities for networking and lead generation. In the last edition of IFE, 82% of our attendees had purchasing authority, making them valuable prospects for your business. Interactions at in-person events allow for immediate connections and potential collaborations. [https://event.montgomerygroup.com/i/amf_angus_montgomery/project_27/Images/3.png?size=340x0&w=BxR_F8Cr6rpt_WUUY4KEtrQkw6yE] Increased Sales and Conversions: Face-to-face interactions allow for more personalised sales pitches, customised solutions, and direct engagement with potential clients, increasing the likelihood of conversion. Plus, IFE provides the best opportunity for buyers to touch, taste, and feel your products directly leading to faster decision-making processes. Sample Buyers List<https://event.montgomerygroup.com/c/1fBspBGLuSAzysj06uCx0uw4> Request Sales Brochure<https://event.montgomerygroup.com/c/1fBsM5OlKh5zn4k4YrckbDCd> Hundreds of companies have already confirmed their participation, why haven't you? [https://event.montgomerygroup.com/i/amf_angus_montgomery/project_27/Images/IFE_exhibitor_logos.png?size=1200x0&w=B-KMRgcHu0_hoCQ-yD02tVWcQQlI] <https://event.montgomerygroup.com/c/1fBt8zVVZFAzbGl9QnM7mMIm> Hear what one of our exhibitors thought about IFE this year... "This was our first year at IFE and the quality of people who have been by our stand had been fantastic. IFE has opened up some channels that we were hoping for but also some completely new ones that we didn’t even think about. It has definitely surpassed our expectations, we have met some great distributors, retailers, wholesalers, potential suppliers and a really interesting mix of people from the UK and abroad. We look forward to returning next year." Corina Donohoe, Director of Business Development, Keto Baker What are you waiting for? Reply directly to this email to secure your stand and find out how IFE can help accelerate your business to the next level.

TextBody: Dear sir If you are running a business that is related to dryers for dried pet food, agricultural or marine products (fish, fruit, etc.) or interested about it, please reach out to SINIL DRYER CO., LTD. in South Korea. We are currently looking for expansion of our business in your country and looking for exclusive distributors to have great business partnership opportunities with us and to grow together. We also provide technology skill which is needed to produce our products. This is our main item - It is difficult to dry natural sea breeze due to fine dust and air pollution. Clean and healthy drying is possible with a marine cold air dryer. We not only supply products, but also provide know-how, production parts and all the necessary raw materials directly. We provide the technology using which the product can be produced locally. We, SINIL DRYER CO., LTD. are incorporated in 2006 and become major company in dryer for agricultural & marine products. TextBody: Dear Sir , Greetings from SKYFRAME EVENTS FZE (EUROPE). Please find enclosed our company profile for your stand design and development at ANUGA 2023 scheduled to be held at Cologne Germany 7-11 October 2023 . Kindly also find our design brief form attached with this mail which will enable us to understand your stand design requirements better . At SKYFRAME EVENTS FZE, we are committed to providing world-class services to help our clients create successful trade shows that meet their exhibition goals, attract the right audience, and boost their brand recognition. Here's what makes us stand out: 1. In-house production facilities in UAE, KSA, Germany, Italy, USA, and Bangladesh. 2. Currently providing services to over 200 exhibitors worldwide. 3. Skyframe Events FZE is a renowned brand in the Middle East and Europe trade show industry, with a reputation for delivering high-quality services to meet the unique needs of our clients. Our in-house production facilities in multiple locations enable us to provide cost-effective and timely services without compromising on quality. We have a team of experienced and talented exhibition stand designers who work closely with our clients to create stand designs that perfectly reflect their brand values, exhibition goals, and investments. Our focus is on delivering value to our clients, and we are proud to have a long list of regular clients who rely on us for their trade show needs. We invite you to partner with us for your next trade show event and experience the SKYFRAME EVENTS FZE difference! Subject: french fries
TextBody: Dear, Thank you for your email and your interest in our company. We also got an e-mail from your colleague Jasper but at Agristo we have decided to focus on working directly with end buyers, as we believe this will provide the best value to our customers and ultimately drive the success of our business. Unfortunately, this means that we will not be able to work with intermediaries such as yourself. The reason behind this decision is that by working directly with the end buyers we can have a better understanding of the market trends and have more control over the prices and terms of the transactions. This will also allow us to have a direct relationship with our customers which we believe will be beneficial for both parties. We would like to thank you for your interest in working with us and hope that you understand our decision.

Subject: Ignite Engagement at Anuga EXPO with Eye-catching LED Walls, Display Splits, and Samsung Signage Displays
TextBody: Rental Price List 2023 [Logo] [Rental Range] ________________________________ Dear Anuga Exhibitor, Thank you for considering RS Media Solutions as your partner for media equipment rentals at your upcoming trade show. We are excited to introduce you to our range of specialized media equipment designed to help you create an impactful booth that captures the attention of attendees. We kindly request that you forward this email to the person in charge of the exhibition planning, ensuring they have access to all the relevant information. Here are the key reasons why RS Media Solutions can make a significant difference for your trade show experience: 1. Expertise and Specialization: With our extensive experience in the field, we understand the unique requirements and challenges faced by exhibitors like you. Our expertise allows us to provide you with the most suitable and technologically advanced equipment, ensuring your booth creates a lasting impact. 2. Wide Range of Options: We offer a diverse selection of media equipment options to customize your booth experience. From LED walls to display splits and single signage displays, we have the perfect solution to match your specific needs, booth size, and budget. 3. Quality and Reliability: Our commitment to delivering exceptional results means we only offer high-quality, meticulously maintained equipment. You can rely on our products without concerns about technical issues or equipment failures during the event. Our inventory consists of professional-grade equipment specifically designed for rental and exhibition usage, ensuring optimal performance and durability. We do not provide equipment intended for home use, guaranteeing that you have access to reliable and industry-standard media solutions for your trade show booth. 4. Customization and Flexibility: We understand that your booth should reflect your brand identity and design preferences. That's why we provide tailored customization options to align the media equipment with your unique requirements. We will collaborate closely with you to adjust size, resolution, or content displayed on the screens, ensuring your booth stands out and effectively communicates your message. 5. Professional Support: Our dedicated support team is available to provide on-site assistance throughout the event. We are experienced in installation, troubleshooting, and content management, allowing you to focus on your core objectives during the trade show. 6. Cost-Effective Solution: We offer competitive pricing for our media equipment rentals. Our transparent pricing structure and flexible rental packages empower you to choose a solution that aligns with your budget without compromising the visual impact and effectiveness of your booth. For our current offers and detailed pricing information, please visit [insert website]. 7. Cost Considerations: Renting directly from the exhibition organizer or stand builder may result in higher costs due to limited competition and potential markup. RS Media Solutions offers competitive pricing for our rentals, along with transparent pricing structures and flexible rental packages. This enables you to choose a cost-effective solution that fits within your budget without compromising the quality or effectiveness of your booth. We highly recommend considering RS Media Solutions as your preferred partner for media equipment rentals. Our combination of expertise, a wide range of options, quality, customization, professional support, and cost-effectiveness makes us the ideal choice for exhibitors like you. To provide you with a glimpse of our current rental offers, we have included an excerpt below this email.

Subject: Frozen French fries supply
TextBody: Hello Simon thank you for reply pls confirm me if you supply FCA terms where can we pick up product ? where we need send truck checked your file , didnt find dry matter of raw material , can u pls specify ? and for frozen goods can we reach dry matter min 32%? also if we make volume to you 100-200 tons per month can we apply price 1-1.1 euro? regards Maria вт, 25 июл. 2023 г. в 17:57, Agristo Sales <sales@agristo.com<mailto:sales@agristo.com>>: Dear Maria, I hope this email finds you well. I am writing to provide you with some essential information regarding Agristo's products, pricing, and specifications. Firstly, it is important to note that Agristo exclusively offers products on a Free Carrier (FCA) basis and does not provide products on an Ex Works (EXW) arrangement. The prices listed in the attached document are based on FCA terms. Agristo takes pride in utilizing various potato varieties in its product range, including notable examples such as Fontane and Challenger. To give you a comprehensive understanding of our products, I have attached an example of Agristo's product specifications. This document outlines key details, including the dry matter content, and includes a visual representation of the product. Regarding pricing, please be aware that the prices listed pertain to products without starch coating and breading coating. For the 10x10 product, the respective prices are 1.36 euros per kilogram for products with starch coating and 1.60 euros per kilogram for products with breading coating. Should you require any further information or have any specific inquiries, please do not hesitate to reach out.

Subject: frozen french fries
TextBody: Hi Benjamin Meire, Thanks very much for your reply. Yes, we bought forzen french fries in our domestic factories in the past and till now. We boutht snow valley, mccain, lambweston and some other brands before.We used snow valley mostly, but from last year, their production line is very tight, often out of stock, this bring us big problem.And for mccain, lambweston is high, half of our customers couldn't accept. So we'd like to find a new factory which could match our requirements. This is the first time we try to purchase the french fries from oversea. We rent a 1000 square meters refrigerated warehouse and our main market is in Wuhan and nearby. Our main product is chicken related products since most of our customers are chain brand burger shops, fried chicken restaurant, and chicken cutlet, except chicken related products, french fries is popular in them. We also have some small distribution partners. We sell about 2000 - 4000 cartons every month. Most are 1/4 cut, very few 3/8 cut. We hope to find a good supplier could provide competitive price and stable goods supply. We hope the french fries could maintain crispness longer since take-away food is very popular here. Could you help advise your price, packing way, lead time and payment term？ Thanks. **************************************************** Company: Wuhan Sinzno Industrial Co., Ltd. Add: Room 703, Building J, Wuhan Salon, No.8 Hongtu Road, Dongxihu District, Wuhan Cell Phone: +86 1898 6263 931​ ------------------原始邮件 ------------------ 发件人:Agristo Sales <sales@agristo.com> 发送时间:07/24/23 19:40:41 收件人:op@sinzno.com <op@sinzno.com> 主题:RE: frozen french fries [ thread::BeINNw-2GZq0IXx6SYPRJ3Q:: ] Dear, Thank you for your email and your interest in our company. Subject: Castle Ingredients at Food Ingredients India Exhibition - Join Us at Booth F71, Hall 1!
TextBody: [https://castle-ingredients.odoo.com/web/image/103552-64907273/mass%20mail%20fii_1.jpg?access_token=217bd44f-8902-4ab2-9a5e-ea10fc21d973] ​We are thrilled to announce that Castle Ingredients will be participating in the upcoming Food Ingredients India (FI India) exhibition, taking place in Mumbai from August 17th to 19th. We cordially invite you to join us at Booth F71 in Hall 1 at the Bombay Exhibition Centre. This event is an excellent opportunity for you to explore our wide range of meticulously crafted high-quality flours and experience our revolutionary Crispy Crystal Rye Cereal firsthand. Our team of experts will be present at the booth to discuss our latest innovations, product offerings, and value-added services tailored to meet the unique needs of the food industry. Mark your calendars and make sure to visit us during the echibition to learn how Catsle Ingredients can elevate your food manufacturing endeavors. Subject: Castle Dairy Belgium  - powder functional dairy blends and powder dairy replacers
TextBody: Dear Madam, Sir, We are Castle Dairy Belgium, a producer of powder functional dairy blends and powder dairy replacers for the food industry. Our products are characterized by a lower and more constant price than the regular SMP and FCMP with often a functional addition for the final product. We have amongst others, products for the ice cream, bakery and chocolate industry. Also Fatfilled Milkpowders which are a substantial part of our portfolio, as well as butter replacers and malt flours. We can pack in 25 kg bags in our brand as well as in Private Label. Please kindly follow the link below in order to discover our range of products: http://castledairy.com/CastleDairyProducts.asp?VD=105&Language=English Please follow the link to discover malt flours. https://www.castlemalting.com/Presentations/CI/CI_MaltFlour_BrochureENG_Reg.pdf I remain at your disposal for any further information that you may need.

Subject: Avoiding Costly Mistakes in Food Packing: Lessons Learned
TextBody: In this email, you will learn more about costly mistakes in food packing. ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ [https://content.app-us1.com/cdn-cgi/image/dpr=2,fit=scale-down,format=auto,onerror=redirect,width=650/WYkQG/2021/07/16/e3fd5507-7b71-4423-9b63-56ab23d2de91.png?r=1889898830] Hello! In the world of food packing, where efficiency, precision, and safety converge, the process itself is a complex dance of intricate steps. The primary objective of manufacturers and producers of food is to guarantee that goods reach consumers in perfect condition while making the most efficient use of resources and cutting costs. But navigating this difficult environment is not without obstacles. Every miscalculation in the packaging process, whether due to technical problems or insufficient equipment, has the potential to be expensive and harmful to the organization. We have looked into the valuable lessons learned from the food packing industry. By examining the critical areas of automation, technical errors, and equipment suitability, we have uncovered key strategies to help us avoid potential pitfalls and build a robust packing operation. Want to learn more about how to avoid these mistakes? Subject: Business Meeting
TextBody: Dear Sir or Madam, My name is Ziad Tabra, and I am the Head of procurement at Good Line Food Supply. Our company is located in Iraq and Kurdistan region. We specialize in supplying food products to hotels, restaurants, and supermarkets throughout Iraq. We are also franchisees of well-established and renowned brands from around the world such as: * Tyson Food * Certified Angus Beef * Martin's potato rolls * Siblou * Jan van as * Cheetos * Vonk culinary cheese * Al Taghziah * Ocean Nest Our research regarding French fries in Iraq has led us to your esteemed company. We are highly interested in procuring French fries in bulk quantities from your organization. We have been impressed by the quality and variety of your products, which have garnered a stellar reputation in the market. Your French fries exhibit exceptional processing, an authentic taste, and a consistent texture. Given the increasing demand for high-quality frozen food products in our target market, we see great potential for collaboration. At Good Line Food Supply, we are recognized for our customer-centric approach and our commitment to offering top-notch products. We place great emphasis on establishing long-term partnerships and strive to expand our business operations. Our aim is to provide our customers with the best possible offerings while upholding the highest standards of quality, availability, and logistics. We would be very happy to arrange a personal meeting at your company. Additionally, our CEO will be in Europe during the period 15.08. to 22.08.2023. Please understand that I am asking for an appointment for the mentioned date. It would be a great pleasure to have the opportunity to meet you in person.

Subject: Export Mexico
TextBody: Dear , Thank you for your email and your interest in our company. At Agristo we have decided to focus on working directly with end buyers, as we believe this will provide the best value to our customers and ultimately drive the success of our business. Unfortunately, this means that we will not be able to work with intermediaries such as yourself. The reason behind this decision is that by working directly with the end buyers we can have a better understanding of the market trends and have more control over the prices and terms of the transactions. This will also allow us to have a direct relationship with our customers which we believe will be beneficial for both parties. We would like to thank you for your interest in working with us and hope that you understand our decision.

We take pride in providing you with the highest quality produce at competitive prices, straight from the farms in Egypt. We are excited to announce that we have expanded our services to the Global market, bringing you a wide range of delicious and nutrient-rich products. From potatoes and onions to apples and strawberries, we’ve got you covered. Our produce is carefully selected, harvested, and transported to ensure it arrives at your doorstep at its freshest. At First Choice Egypt, we believe in the power of nature and the benefits it brings to our health and wellbeing. Our products are packed with essential vitamins and minerals, and have been known to improve digestion, reduce inflammation, and support brain function. We offer our titles in both English and Arabic, making it easier for you to navigate our website and choose from our wide range of products. We are committed to providing you with exceptional customer service and ensuring your satisfaction with every purchase. Thank you for choosing First Choice Egypt as your trusted source for fresh and healthy produce. We look forward to serving you and bringing a taste of Egypt to your doorstep.

Subject: BRITISH FOOD
TextBody: Hallo, Ik zie dat Zoë in verlof is. Ik kreeg dit mailtje binnen van een klant. Kan er iemand dit opvolgen? Alvast bedankt! Subject: Inquiry for Frozen French Fries - Dama Kuwait
TextBody: Dear Saleem, Thank you for providing me with all the necessary information. As I mentionned in my previous email, we only set up a private label starting from 500 tons per SKU. See here below our general conditions: MOQ of 500 ton per SKU per year We ask a financial guarantee of € 2000 per SKU to start up. After the MOQ is exceeded we transfer this amount back. Agristo will arrange everything to produce the foil with our partners. Designs come from the customer If the design is ready, it takes up to 2 months for the foil to be ready to go into production Afterwards if expected volumes are clear we could make sure to have a minimum volume on stock so it would take 1 week then from order to delivery. We kindly request a comprehensive monthly forecast from your end. Understanding your projections is crucial for effective planning. If your annual requirement is limited to 15 containers, it would not accumulate to the extent of 500 tons per product. Therefore, sharing your forecasting with us is of significant importance. If setting up a private label is not feasible for you, we can always first start working with one of our own brands. Let me know your feedback on this and do not hesitate to contact me if you have any questions.

Subject: Frozen French fries supply
TextBody: Dag Benjamin, Onderstaande een interessante Lead voor Rusland. Het hoofdkantoor van de Lead is in Sint-Petersburg en ze leveren aan fast food restaurants in Moskou en Sint-Petersburg. Het volume dat ze willen aankopen ligt tussen de 100-200 ton per maand. Aangezien Rusland toch een "speciaal" geval is het beter dat jij er zelf even naar kijkt. Ik ben volgende week opreis maar indien je info nodig hebt kan je mij altijd bellen. TextBody: IE士資格取得講座 [http://img03.en25.com/EloquaImages/clients/JMAEloqua01/%7B20f978c2-ec6e-41a9-a2a3-2f5c93e4cd44%7D_logo.png]<https://s1673224453.t.en25.com/e/er?utm_campaign=3270532705230824_%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A3%E3%83%97%E3%83%AD%EF%BC%9A%E3%82%AA%E3%83%A0%E3%83%AD%E3%83%B32&s=1673224453&lid=5372&elqTrackId=7F8EBFDD31ADB803CACB56EA49567F2A&elq=ee2fbaff8aa046768185ae68e9bd9fbe&elqaid=32705&elqat=1> データサイエンスだけでは「現場の事象と合わない」 現場改善だけでは「大きな成果につながりにくい」 データと現場をつなぐ人材として『IE士』が注目されています！ 10月開講！申込受付中！ 【残り数枠】お問い合わせください！ 『IE士資格』取得ができるのは 生産革新プロフェッショナルコースだけ 当研修はIE(インダストリアル・エンジニアリング)をこれから学ぼうとしている方向けの研修ではありませんが、無料特典講義でIEの基礎知識の補完や学び直しができますのでご安心ください。 当講義では、開発・生産・調達・物流のバリューチェーン全体を俯瞰した改善やマネジメントなどを体得していきます。 非常に幅広い大手、中堅、中小企業からご派遣をいただいています。 過去の受講企業はこちら：https://jma-iepro.com/program<https://s1673224453.t.en25.com/e/er?utm_campaign=3270532705230824_%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A3%E3%83%97%E3%83%AD%EF%BC%9A%E3%82%AA%E3%83%A0%E3%83%AD%E3%83%B32&s=1673224453&lid=8450&elqTrackId=22FA6E5169DE5EA1B044D83A02D7B590&elq=ee2fbaff8aa046768185ae68e9bd9fbe&elqaid=32705&elqat=1> 【オムロン インタビュー その2】 なぜ今、「自分」にとって「会社」にとってIEが必要だったのか？ オムロン株式会社 IABカンパニー 生産SCM本部 生産革新センタ 生産技術部 鍋島 広昭 様に、 「生産革新プロフェッショナルコース」受講の背景やご活用についてお伺いしました。 （※以降敬称略、所属・役職は2023年1月19日時点） [http://img03.en25.com/EloquaImages/clients/JMAEloqua01/%7Bd67c531e-4997-4cab-b842-b8edf5eb72b5%7D_omron2.jpg] 鍋島： 上司から「こういう研修があるよ」と教えてもらいました。概要を見るとまさに自身の業務に直結する内容であり、受講を決めました。生産技術と言えばIEですし、工程分析の言葉自体は知ってはいましたが、しっかり学びたいという意気込みで研修に臨みました。知らない手法、方向性、考え方が…… 続きはこちら 〉<https://s1673224453.t.en25.com/e/er?utm_campaign=3270532705230824_%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A3%E3%83%97%E3%83%AD%EF%BC%9A%E3%82%AA%E3%83%A0%E3%83%AD%E3%83%B32&s=1673224453&lid=19789&elqTrackId=31C7966443BB67D7F5AFDFF4A3B6E279&elq=ee2fbaff8aa046768185ae68e9bd9fbe&elqaid=32705&elqat=1> ホームページにて随時公開! ①オートメーションで「よりよい社会」をつくる。発展の求心力は創業から変わらない考え方 ②なぜ今、「自分」にとって「会社」にとってIEが必要だったのか？ ③自働化は目的ではない！研修を通してIEの必要性を再認識 ④IEの知識だけではなかった！一人だけではできない、人を活かすための学びとは？ 当研修を受講されて活躍されている『IE士の皆様』の 事例・インタビュー記事をHPにて公開しています！ 京セラ、タニタ秋田、大成建設、東京電力HD、グローブライド、ノーリツ…多数！ ・自社の魅力や強み ・受講前に抱いていた組織の課題 ・参加までの障壁 ・受講の感想や変化 研 修 概 要 会 期： 2023年10月6日(金) ～ 12月15日(金) ■講 義： ・受講満足度95％以上、アーカイブによる動画学習とリアルタイムのオンライン講習が基本線 ・次年度リアルを主とした単位も実施！ ※認定試験、IEインストラクター演習はリアル開催 ※逐次、受講生される皆様、企業様からご要望を次第でリアルの場も検討しています。 ※開講式（オリエン）はハイブリッドを予定 ■最終試験の受験会場： 日本能率協会 研修室（東京都港区）を予定 ※試験については、毎年リアル（実地）開催 ■対 象： 生産・製造部門のマネージャー・リーダーとその候補者 物流・設備管理のマネージャー・リーダーとその候補者 社内研修講師 ものづくり教育担当 ※対象者にご不安がありましたらお気軽にご相談ください。調達、物流部門からもご参加いただいています。 ※近年、製造業以外の企業からもご参加いただいています。 【ご参考情報】 受講者層のボリュームゾーンは業歴10～15年以上の方々 近年では業歴20年以上の方も、非常に多くご受講 ■受講目的（キャリアステップの一例） ・管理職、ベテラン →社内の工場診断士、社内講師、全社の改善、革新に関わる企業幹部 ・中堅、次期ベテラン、次期管理職候補 →生産性向上・生産革新のリーダー、組織の管理職 ■参加料（税込）：※残り数枠！お問い合わせください！ 日本能率協会 法人会員 ：693,000円/人 法人会員外 ：748,000円/人 ■無料特典講義（閉講まで何度でも受講可） ・IE基礎テクニック習得コース（約24時間分） ・IE基礎分析手法習得セミナー（約2.5時間分） ■IE士について 当研修を修了し、所定の成績を修めた方に「IE士」という認定資格が付与されます。 パンフレットはこちら Subject: request for potatoes to Georgia country freanch
TextBody: Dear Avi, Thank you for providing me with the necessary information. At Agristo we have decided to focus on working directly with end buyers, as we believe this will provide the best value to our customers and ultimately drive the success of our business. Unfortunately, this means that we will not be able to work with intermediaries such as yourself. The reason behind this decision is that by working directly with the end buyers we can have a better understanding of the market trends and have more control over the prices and terms of the transactions. This will also allow us to have a direct relationship with our customers which we believe will be beneficial for both parties. We would like to thank you for your interest in working with us and hope that you understand our decision.

Subject: Your Participation @ ANUGA 2023 - Cologne
TextBody: Hello Warm regards! This mail is regarding your participation in " ANUGA 2023 " at Messe Cologne, Germany from Sat, 07 Oct, 2023 - Wed, 11 Oct, 2023. We specialize and provide you our best services in Stand Designing and Construction with economy and creativity, so that you have the least botheration. We have a reputed name in the field of Exhibition & Events with experience of more than two decades. Kindly click on our company profile<https://drive.google.com/file/d/14f429omU198_PVsx3uNG73X-LJfnRJRy/view?usp=sharing> along with some images of our past successful work executed globally. Moreover, We would also like share some of our recent successful delivered stands in 2023.<https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Gf08mov0lTJtVr12o_FDEPmZUIqOTj2D/view?pli=1> This will also help you to put faith in our services. Looking forward to the pleasure of serving you and assuring you with our best quality work and services. Kindly give us an opportunity by fill this exhibitor brief form along with the layout of your booth in order to submit some attractive design options with our best possible quotation for your ANUGA 2023 stand. EXHIBITOR REQUIREMENTS FORM FOR BOOTH DESIGNING & FABRICATION STAND DETAILS 1 Hall No 2 Stand No 3 Stand Size (L x W) 4 Type of stand (wooden or modular/shell scheme) 5 Open Side of the Stand ( 1 Side, 2 Side, 3 Side or Island ) 6 Any particular color theme for the stand design 7 Type of flooring (Carpet / Wooden Finish) & (raised or un-raised) 8 Double story/ Mezzanine stand (Y/N) 9 Reception Counter Required (Y/N). 10 Closed Meeting Room Required (Y/N). 11 Open sitting Area Required (Y/N). 12 Sofa Set with Center Glass Table Required (Y/N). 13 Glass Round Table + Chairs or Bar Stool Required (Y/N). If Y, how many 14 LCD with DVD Player Required ( Y/N ) If Y, how many 15 Pantry / Storage Area Required ( Y/N ) 16 Electric kettle / Coffee Vending Machine ( Y/N ) 17 Refrigerator ( Y/N ) DISPLAY PRODUCT DETAILS 1 Product Display Podiums ( Y/N ) If Y, how many ? 2 Nature of the products to be displayed 3 No. of Products to be displayed, 4 Product Dimensions, Specifications ( Images will be helpful) BRANDING DETAILS 1 Company Logo ( Must Required) 2 No. of Posters Required 3 Brochure Stand Required ( Y/N ) 4 Tentative Budget 5 Your company web address NOTE Kindly send previous stand images if available. Thanks Francesco Russo - Marketing al. Jerozolimskie 85/21, 02-001 Warszawa Poland +48 22 1530 666

Subject: Uganda International Trade Fair
TextBody: [https://mcusercontent.com/98a0b864fe7802e2d098c8d4e/images/5ba93b71-e4a1-7efd-2388-194556cc24f7.jpg] Once again, It is indeed our great pleasure to invite you to participate at the forthcoming 29th Uganda Trade Fair' 2023, Biggest & Largest annual International Trade Fair on all kinds of general, FMCG, consumer and industrial products be held from 4 - 8 October 2023 at the Lugogo Show Grounds Hall 1, 2, 3 & 4 located in the centre of Kampala, Uganda. Over 500 Companies are participating from 18 Countries As of today we have only (7) stands available in the INTERNATIONAL HALL # 1 as Hall No 2, 3 & 4 are fully booked. Below is the list of Available stands for your kind attention. Kindly note that Stands are limited and booking will be only on first come first serve basis. Kindly fill the Participation Booking Application Form with your require options and email it back to us before 10th September. AVAILABLE STANDS STAND # A19 - 18 m2 (6m x 3m) STAND # E7 - 18 m2 (6m x 3m) STAND # A16 - 9 m2 (3m x 3m) STAND # A17 - 9 m2 (3m x 3m) STAND # A18 - 9 m2 (3m x 3m) STAND # E9 - 9 m2 (3m x 3m) STAND # E10 - 9 m2 (3m x 3m) We have DESIGNED SPECIAL PACKAGE FOR EXHIBITOR'S (ONLY FOR UAE COMPANIES) * 9sq.m shell stand (3m x 3m) with basic furniture such as 2 chairs, 1 Table, 2 Spotlights, 1 Twin Power Socket * Company Name panel with logo & country flag on Fascia * Brief listing in official show catalogue * 7 Days / 6 Nights 5***** Hotel Accommodation including daily breakfast & all room tax & VAT * Business Visa for Uganda. * Return Economy class Air Ticket to (Dubai - Kampala - Dubai) Uganda. (Emirates / Fly Dubai) * Personnel assistant on arrival at Entebbe Intl Airport * Airport picks up & drop * Separate car with professional tour driver for 5 Days so that you can easily meet your clients & study the market * 1 Local Stand assistant Girl for 5 Days during the expo * Useful data of major 400 importers of Uganda enable you to send invitation through email / whatsapp to pre-plan your meeting COST OF ABOVE FULL PACKAGE IS Option 1 - One person with Single room AED 21,500 Option 2 - Two persons with One Double room AED 28,500 Option 3 - Two persons with Two Single rooms AED 33,500 We also have DESIGNED SPECIAL PACKAGE FOR VISITOR'S (ONLY FOR UAE COMPANIES) * 5 Days / 4 Nights 5***** Hotel Accommodation including daily breakfast & all room tax & VAT * Business Visa for Uganda. * Return Economy class Air Ticket to (Dubai - Kampala - Dubai) Uganda. (Emirates / Fly Dubai) * Personnel assistant on arrival at Entebbe Intl Airport * Airport picks up & drop * Daily transportation from hotel to expo center & back * Expo entry pass will be provided. COST OF ABOVE PACKAGE IS Option 1 - One person with Single room AED 6,500 Option 2 - Two persons with One Double room AED 11,000 CLICK HERE TO DOWNLOAD BOOKING FORM<https://inexpos.us10.list-manage.com/track/click?u=b5f018450c6b52ec118ebbe0d&id=86dda165d6&e=dbc3a3ad4e> In the above link you will find the following useful info such as; * Exhibitor's Booking Application Form * Trade Visitor Booking Application Form * Useful Information & Products Profile * Floor Plan with available stand locations for your selection * Exhibitors List * Photo Gallery enable you to understand how the stands will be look alike. LAST YEAR SUMMARY & STATISTICS 28th Uganda Intl Trade Fair 2022 was officially inaugurated by the President of Uganda H.E. Yoweri Kaguta Museveni along with the Minister of Trade & Industry with a massive group of various Ambassadors, Diplomats and Head of Major Government departments. 732 Companies participated from 24 Countries such as Austria, Bahrain, China, Egypt, Ghana, Hong Kong, India, Indonesia, Iran, Italy, Japan, Jordan, Kenya, Malaysia, Pakistan, Rwanda, Saudi Arabia, Senegal, South Africa, Taiwan, Tanzania, Thailand, Turkey, UAE & Uganda. 75% Visitors are from Uganda and between 12-14 % trade buyers will come from Neighbouring countries such as Rwanda, Congo, Djibouti, Somaliland, Sudan, Kenya, Tanzania, Uganda, Morocco, Tunisia, and around 10% visitors will be coming from Saudi Arabia, Oman, India, Kuwait, Italy, Indonesia, Egypt & Turkey. With over 45 Million population, Uganda is become one of the most attractive and potential export markets in East Africa for the Foreign Companies. The Ugandan economy has been escalating regularly. According to our previous experience and market survey, we foresee a tremendous response at the exhibition for all sectors since Uganda imports almost everything. We wish you the very best in your business and look forward to welcome you at Uganda Trade Fair' 2023. For any further information, please feel free to contact on my mobile +97155 – 5506187. Thanks &

Subject: Products inquiry.
TextBody: Dear Sir, We are a UK based Import and Export company interested to do business with you. I have got your company's contact through my search for reliable suppliers and I am writing to bring to your notice that I am seeking for manufacturers, wholesalers and suppliers who would be interested in supplying their products to us at competitive prices. Be kind to send me the below information. 1) Your Current Catalog/Product List 2) Your price list in FOB or EX-WORKS/EX-FACTORY 3) Your company profile if any You may include any information that will help me learn more about your products. In your reply let us know if you have a sales outlet in London or an agent so as to deal directly with them, otherwise we will transact with you directly and conclude the order. We are sincerely looking forward to working with you. Regards Saifudheen Anees General Manager Sharafco Trading Co.,LLC

Subject: Supply your fresh produce to Dubai!
TextBody: Meet top fruit & vegetable wholesalers and retailers in the Middle East market! Boost Your Exports In 2023 View email in your browser<https://mailchi.mp/8683d47b1b64/supply-your-fresh-produce-to-dubai?e=57d53fc4cd> [Organic] <https://organicandnatural.us17.list-manage.com/track/click?u=4a8fc3f71f4fa284093a69a7a&id=a70eb1a5e8&e=57d53fc4cd> [Organic] <https://organicandnatural.us17.list-manage.com/track/click?u=4a8fc3f71f4fa284093a69a7a&id=1775eb6d5d&e=57d53fc4cd> [img-1] Spread over an area of more than 66,000 square meters, the Bloom market is one of the biggest indoor markets in the region. With more than 760+ kiosks and traders from all around the world present here, this market serves as a sourcing hub for the B2B buyers in the Middle East. Download Market Information<https://organicandnatural.us17.list-manage.com/track/click?u=4a8fc3f71f4fa284093a69a7a&id=bf7aae3a8c&e=57d53fc4cd> [https://mcusercontent.com/4a8fc3f71f4fa284093a69a7a/images/3f9640f0-1225-1242-a625-0b364acfb9a1.png] In the last few years, we have observed niche customers forming in the Middle East who are willing to pay a premium price for healthy and exotic fruits. We can see a hike in demand especially for fresh produce in our hypermarkets. The cost of local produce has risen almost by 40% in the last few years, this is the best time for exporters to enter this market! [https://mcusercontent.com/4a8fc3f71f4fa284093a69a7a/images/af3b0504-ecac-1f04-dc3e-377ea62b9411.png] [img-2] How do we help you meet these buyers? Subject: potato for kosovo
TextBody: Dear, Thank you for your email and your interest in our company. To evaluate your request, we want to get a better picture of your company. Could you inform us and give some detailed information regarding: Do you already purchase frozen (potato) products? What is your experience in this field? If yes, with what brands or companies do you already work? Why do you wish to change? What volumes of fries per SKU do you do annually? Do you have your own distribution channel or partners? And warehouses? Could you provide me some more information concerning your company? Do you have a website? What is your market strategy? Who are your customers? If you have any further questions, please do not hesitate to contact us. With

Subject: UAE in Uganda
TextBody: [https://mcusercontent.com/98a0b864fe7802e2d098c8d4e/images/5ba93b71-e4a1-7efd-2388-194556cc24f7.jpg] Once again, It is indeed our great pleasure to invite you to participate at the forthcoming 29th Uganda Trade Fair' 2023, Biggest & Largest annual International Trade Fair on all kinds of general, FMCG, consumer and industrial products be held from 4 - 8 October 2023 at the Lugogo Show Grounds Hall 1, 2, 3 & 4 located in the centre of Kampala, Uganda. Over 500 Companies are participating from 18 Countries As of today we have only (7) stands available in the INTERNATIONAL HALL # 1 as Hall No 2, 3 & 4 are fully booked. Below is the list of Available stands for your kind attention. Kindly note that Stands are limited and booking will be only on first come first serve basis. Kindly fill the Participation Booking Application Form with your require options and email it back to us before 10th September. AVAILABLE STANDS STAND # A19 - 18 m2 (6m x 3m) STAND # E7 - 18 m2 (6m x 3m) STAND # A16 - 9 m2 (3m x 3m) STAND # A17 - 9 m2 (3m x 3m) STAND # A18 - 9 m2 (3m x 3m) STAND # E9 - 9 m2 (3m x 3m) STAND # E10 - 9 m2 (3m x 3m) We have DESIGNED SPECIAL PACKAGE FOR EXHIBITOR'S (ONLY FOR UAE COMPANIES) * 9sq.m shell stand (3m x 3m) with basic furniture such as 2 chairs, 1 Table, 2 Spotlights, 1 Twin Power Socket * Company Name panel with logo & country flag on Fascia * Brief listing in official show catalogue * 7 Days / 6 Nights 5***** Hotel Accommodation including daily breakfast & all room tax & VAT * Business Visa for Uganda. * Return Economy class Air Ticket to (Dubai - Kampala - Dubai) Uganda. (Emirates / Fly Dubai) * Personnel assistant on arrival at Entebbe Intl Airport * Airport picks up & drop * Separate car with professional tour driver for 5 Days so that you can easily meet your clients & study the market * 1 Local Stand assistant Girl for 5 Days during the expo * Useful data of major 400 importers of Uganda enable you to send invitation through email / whatsapp to pre-plan your meeting COST OF ABOVE FULL PACKAGE IS Option 1 - One person with Single room AED 21,500 Option 2 - Two persons with One Double room AED 28,500 Option 3 - Two persons with Two Single rooms AED 33,500 We also have DESIGNED SPECIAL PACKAGE FOR VISITOR'S (ONLY FOR UAE COMPANIES) * 5 Days / 4 Nights 5***** Hotel Accommodation including daily breakfast & all room tax & VAT * Business Visa for Uganda. * Return Economy class Air Ticket to (Dubai - Kampala - Dubai) Uganda. (Emirates / Fly Dubai) * Personnel assistant on arrival at Entebbe Intl Airport * Airport picks up & drop * Daily transportation from hotel to expo center & back * Expo entry pass will be provided. COST OF ABOVE PACKAGE IS Option 1 - One person with Single room AED 6,500 Option 2 - Two persons with One Double room AED 11,000 CLICK HERE TO DOWNLOAD BOOKING FORM<https://inexpos.us10.list-manage.com/track/click?u=b5f018450c6b52ec118ebbe0d&id=e2b5f5fd72&e=dbc3a3ad4e> In the above link you will find the following useful info such as; * Exhibitor's Booking Application Form * Trade Visitor Booking Application Form * Useful Information & Products Profile * Floor Plan with available stand locations for your selection * Exhibitors List * Photo Gallery enable you to understand how the stands will be look alike. LAST YEAR SUMMARY & STATISTICS 28th Uganda Intl Trade Fair 2022 was officially inaugurated by the President of Uganda H.E. Yoweri Kaguta Museveni along with the Minister of Trade & Industry with a massive group of various Ambassadors, Diplomats and Head of Major Government departments. 732 Companies participated from 24 Countries such as Austria, Bahrain, China, Egypt, Ghana, Hong Kong, India, Indonesia, Iran, Italy, Japan, Jordan, Kenya, Malaysia, Pakistan, Rwanda, Saudi Arabia, Senegal, South Africa, Taiwan, Tanzania, Thailand, Turkey, UAE & Uganda. 75% Visitors are from Uganda and between 12-14 % trade buyers will come from Neighbouring countries such as Rwanda, Congo, Djibouti, Somaliland, Sudan, Kenya, Tanzania, Uganda, Morocco, Tunisia, and around 10% visitors will be coming from Saudi Arabia, Oman, India, Kuwait, Italy, Indonesia, Egypt & Turkey. With over 45 Million population, Uganda is become one of the most attractive and potential export markets in East Africa for the Foreign Companies. The Ugandan economy has been escalating regularly. According to our previous experience and market survey, we foresee a tremendous response at the exhibition for all sectors since Uganda imports almost everything. We wish you the very best in your business and look forward to welcome you at Uganda Trade Fair' 2023. For any further information, please feel free to contact on my mobile +97155 – 5506187. Thanks &

Subject: 26ème Salon "Monte-Carlo Gastronomie 2023" à Monaco Principauté
TextBody: [cid:image006.png@01D99ED4.3514EF00] Bonjour, La 26ème édition du Salon "MONTE-CARLO GASTRONOMIE" ouvrira ses portes du 24 au 27 Novembre 2023 au Chapiteau de Fontvieille de la Principauté de Monaco. Si vous souhaitez recevoir un dossier d'information, afin de considérer votre éventuelle participation, merci de bien vouloir nous envoyer une demande en répondant par e-mail. Merci de mentionner également votre adresse postale, votre téléphone ainsi que votre site web. Nous vous l'enverrons au plus vite. Après l'interruption due à la pandémie du covid-19, le Salon « Monte-Carlo Gastronomie » a réuni l'année dernière une sélection des meilleurs produits agroalimentaires français, italiens et européens, avec un grand succès public et toujours l’organisation des deux concours culinaires, pour les amateurs « Maestro Chef » et pour les enfants « Maestro Kid », dans un cadre convivial et raffiné et des visiteurs fidélisés et à haut pouvoir d'achat. Comme chaque année un espace animation sera consacré au grand public et aux professionnels du monde de la gastronomie, avec la participation active de plusieurs grands Chefs de la Région tels que: Joël Garault Chef et Président de l’Association « Monaco Goût et Saveurs », Pascal Garrigues Chef du « Monte-Carlo Beach », Laurent Collin Chef du « Méridien Beach Plaza Monte-Carlo », Laurent Sturbois et Patrice Guillet Chefs du « Café de Paris », Jean-Claude Brugel et Luc Gamel Chefs MOF, Jean-Laurent Basile Chef des « Thermes Marins de Monte-Carlo », Frédéric Ramos Chef du « Novotel de Monaco », Richard Ruppe Chef du « Sans Souci de Monaco », Gian Luca Strobino Chef de l’ « Hôtel de Paris », Marc Maccari Chef de l’Ambassade de France à Monaco, Benoit Witz Chef de l’ « Hôtel Hermitage », Dominique Milardi, Chef Sommelier du « Méridien Beach Plaza Monte-Carlo » et Président de l’Association Monégasque des Sommeliers, Antonio Fochi Premier Maître d’Hôtel du « Méridien Beach Plaza Monte-Carlo », … De nombreuses associations professionnelles sont également très impliquées, à l’instar du Slow Food Monaco Riviera Cote D'azur avec le Prix “Slow Food” et le Prix des Chroniqueurs Gastronomiques qui prime les producteurs de vins et de champagne. L’Association Monégasque des Sommeliers, l’Association de Maîtres d’Hôtels Italiens et Français, l’Association des Barmen de Monaco, l’Académie Nationale de Cuisine de Nice, la Confrérie de l’Etiquette du Mentonnais, le Grand Cordon d’Or, Monaco Goût et Saveurs, l’Association de l’Industrie Hôtelière Monégasque, participent également activement au Salon. Cette manifestation bénéficie d’une forte médiatisation qui s’étend de la Côte d’Azur à la Riviera Italienne. Dans l’attente de votre aimable retour, je me tiens à votre disposition pour toute information complémentaire et vous prie d’agréer, Madame, Monsieur, l’assurance de mes sincères salutations Giorgio Gandolfi responsable commercial Monte-Carlo Gastronomie Athos Palace - 2, rue de la Lüjerneta MC 98000 Monaco t. +377 97 98 50 00 https://montecarlogastronomie.com/ https://www.facebook.com/MonteCarloGastronomie/ https://www.instagram.com/montecarlogastronomie/

Subject: PRESENTATION OF INTERCOP
TextBody: Dear Sir/Madam, INTERCOP, provides national and international complete logistic services incorporating air, sea, rail and land transport, full warehousing and distribution facilities, container and related intermodal and global supporting services that supports the Freight Forwarding Wing. [Europa y África en globo terráqueo]Global Operations: Operations & Custom Clearance: end to end logistic services with and under a single point of contact. [Camión]Specialized Transport Logistic: Rapid and effective to move cargo from port to warehouse and /or directly to your customers. Services can be combined or tailored to meet individual client´s needs. Traditional Container & Pallets Transport: Specialized logistic handling and delivery of any products, services include transportation and logistics container management. Warehousing and storage for food grade, hazardous & non-hazardous goods, land, sea and air freight delivery. [Escena de puente]Seamless end to end cross docking facilities: Solutions for quick perfect dispatch Solutions for any unique or abnormal/wide-load and fragile items. Warehousing: [Carro]Spacious own warehouse and machineries with all modes of distributions makes our warehouse synergies the best in the business. Thank you for having taken the time to read our presentation. Waiting to hear and be at your service in a very near future. P.S. Intercop has started on a new project due to urge of clients that want to send things back home via Groupage Service, and we wonder if you would like to participate with other cargo agents at your side, that would send them to the Canaries to be re-routed to African Countries.

Subject: Fairfilm ANUGA 2023
TextBody: Dear AGRISTO nv -Team, We are a production company for audiovisual media, situated in Wuppertal, with over 10 years of experience in the fields of culture and events. We would like to produce an individual short film (20-60 sec.) for you, which will give the viewer a first impression of your products and services at the ANUGA 2023, perfectly suited for the presentation on your online- and social-media channels. In addition to the professional video- and audio recordings, we are offering a bundle package with 10 photographs for a small surcharge. Of course, we can provide you with extra photos. The flat-rate fee is 10 EUR per photo (plus VAT). If you accept the offer, our team will record footage of your booth as well as footage containing your product highlights and combine it in a short video clip. The production of the short film without the photographs will be 350 EUR (plus VAT). The bundle, including the recording of audio and video material, data management, postproduction and the distribution of the final film and photographs, amounts to 450 EUR (plus VAT). We also offer professional voice recordings for your fair trade video for an additional 80 EUR (plus VAT). In order to give you an idea of what your film could look like, we would like to show you three short films that we have produced recently. At the FIBO 2022, we produced an Instagram-clip about innovative training machines for Vitruvian Product Pty LTD. https://vimeo.com/697550320/755fff9ecf At the BioWest 2022 we produced a short promotion video for the food manufacturer Teutoburger Ölmühle GmbH. https://vimeo.com/698585130/0f7c122e5b In order to give you an insight into our projects outside of fair trades, here’s a teaser we produced for the shoe brand Blundstone. https://vimeo.com/716414409/a63ffc6356 As we want to give you a full impression of our field of production, we included this short clip that we produced for the opening ceremony 2022 of the Lehmbruck Museum. https://vimeo.com/692343018/18cc1329a2 We are looking forward to hearing from you! Yours Sincerely Lucy Wecke Exhibition Team Siegersbusch [https://www.siegersbusch.de/logoSignatur.png] [„facebook“] [„instagram“] SIEGERSBUSCH FILM, JEUCKENS/WINDUS GBR, FRIEDRICH-EBERT-STR.143E, 42117 WUPPERTAL TELEFON: 0202 42 99 08 78 TELEFAX: 0202 716 740 18 WWW.SIEGERSBUSCH.DE

Subject: Check-In with Food & Hotel Malaysia 2023
TextBody: Click here<https://s418238.t.en25.com/e/es?s=418238&e=15108&elqTrackId=9a42947388a84f0e8d0267239dc5ddbd&elq=c05d1a652703428499d41213f4333209&elqaid=1037&elqat=1> to view the online version Food and Hotel Malaysia Newsletter [https://gumtgc.stripocdn.email/content/guids/CABINET_7177af465967c545833e4d898b0eff4727c50fbead8001040f15d30579ff510d/images/fhm_edm_header_1458x625px_4.jpg]<https://s418238.t.en25.com/e/er?s=418238&lid=3327&elqTrackId=98dec181a4844bf988db3792eed2618c&elq=c05d1a652703428499d41213f4333209&elqaid=1037&elqat=1> About FHM<https://s418238.t.en25.com/e/er?s=418238&lid=3326&elqTrackId=ca6a54807526450688f3ced64037c76c&elq=c05d1a652703428499d41213f4333209&elqaid=1037&elqat=1> Digital Showroom<https://s418238.t.en25.com/e/er?s=418238&lid=3325&elqTrackId=1ff937c17b574b1bb6affac5b7056cd4&elq=c05d1a652703428499d41213f4333209&elqaid=1037&elqat=1> Visitor Pre-Registration<https://s418238.t.en25.com/e/er?s=418238&lid=3322&elqTrackId=b914994dedac49e88b0f5450fb51c028&elq=c05d1a652703428499d41213f4333209&elqaid=1037&elqat=1> Check-In with Food & Hotel Malaysia 2023 Promoting Sustainability Across the Food and Hospitality Sector At Food and Hotel Malaysia, we're not just an exhibition; we're a platform for transformation. The urgency of sustainability has taken centre stage, and we understand the pivotal role that every industry stakeholder plays in combating the challenges that lie ahead, such as climate change. As a premier global food and hospitality event, we embrace our responsibility to champion sustainable practices. Driven by the ethos of our organisers, Informa Markets, our efforts are aimed at catalysing positive environmental, social and economic progress within our host cities and across the industry at large. Our Commitment to a Greener Future at Food & Hotel Malaysia 2023: * Digital adoption and online registration to reduce paper * E-Show Preview and E-Show Guide * FHM and Food Aid Foundation will launch Food Share to collect surplus food. * Recycling bin segregation and a food waste composting system, a joint effort by FHM and KLCC. ..and more! Play Your Part in Shaping a Sustainable Future [https://gumtgc.stripocdn.email/content/guids/CABINET_7177af465967c545833e4d898b0eff4727c50fbead8001040f15d30579ff510d/images/waste_management256.png] Responsible Waste Management Dispose of food and general waste items conscientiously to minimise your environmental footprint. Properly labelled bins and recycling receptacles will be provided around the venue. [https://gumtgc.stripocdn.email/content/guids/CABINET_7177af465967c545833e4d898b0eff4727c50fbead8001040f15d30579ff510d/images/vehicles04256.png] Opt for Public Transportation Minimise your carbon footprint by utilising public transport or shared car services when commuting the easily accessible KL Convention Centre to FHM 2023. Get the full details here<https://s418238.t.en25.com/e/er?s=418238&lid=3285&elqTrackId=e43e90cd11ed49e282b592416d80576e&elq=c05d1a652703428499d41213f4333209&elqaid=1037&elqat=1>. [https://gumtgc.stripocdn.email/content/guids/CABINET_7177af465967c545833e4d898b0eff4727c50fbead8001040f15d30579ff510d/images/streamline61256.png] Visit the Future Hub Engage with cutting-edge sustainable solutions industry peers to drive sustainability. With your support, we can continually grow our emphasis on sustainability in future. Pre-Register for Free Admission Now<https://s418238.t.en25.com/e/er?s=418238&lid=2287&elqTrackId=65b3039155184398ba964aab91551a58&elq=c05d1a652703428499d41213f4333209&elqaid=1037&elqat=1> Kindly take note that pre-registration (free admission) will close at 5PM, 18 September. All registrations thereafter will be subject to a RM50.00 admission fee. Event Highlights: Future Hub [https://gumtgc.stripocdn.email/content/guids/CABINET_7177af465967c545833e4d898b0eff4727c50fbead8001040f15d30579ff510d/images/untitled_design.jpg] From carbon exchange credit and food waste management to future food, plant-based culinary art and feeding the future, we are proud to present collaborations with Impact Circle, Malaysian Association Of Hotels (MAH), Le Cordon Bleu Malaysia and many others. Location: Future Hub, Hall 7, Level 3 View Future Hub Programme<https://s418238.t.en25.com/e/er?s=418238&lid=3324&elqTrackId=1ff18eee20e743c683989115dd208e16&elq=c05d1a652703428499d41213f4333209&elqaid=1037&elqat=1> Trend Talk [https://gumtgc.stripocdn.email/content/guids/CABINET_7177af465967c545833e4d898b0eff4727c50fbead8001040f15d30579ff510d/images/fhm_36.JPG] A hotspot for industry professionals to dish out the latest culinary trends and freshest hospitality experiences. From gourmet ingredients to personalised services, join the conversation and spice things up by staying ahead of the game in this ever-evolving industry. Location: Trend Talk, Hospitality Lounge 2, Hall 2 View Trend Talk Programme<https://s418238.t.en25.com/e/er?s=418238&lid=3323&elqTrackId=c0189a322b1140918414375ab8e3222b&elq=c05d1a652703428499d41213f4333209&elqaid=1037&elqat=1> Pre-Register for Free Admission Now<https://s418238.t.en25.com/e/er?s=418238&lid=3322&elqTrackId=3521c13d97f34dc6bbc143248597b590&elq=c05d1a652703428499d41213f4333209&elqaid=1037&elqat=1> Kindly take note that pre-registration (free admission) will close at 5PM, 18 September. All registrations thereafter will be subject to a RM50.00 admission fee. Enrich Your Experience at FHM 2023 [https://gumtgc.stripocdn.email/content/guids/CABINET_7177af465967c545833e4d898b0eff4727c50fbead8001040f15d30579ff510d/images/aa.png] Experience a Seamless Visit to FHM with AirAsia Ride! Save more with promo code FHM2023 and enjoy RM3 off on your first 2 rides to or from Kuala Lumpur Convention Centre. Don't miss out! *T&C apply. Here’s a 3-step guide to stand a chance to win prizes at FHM 2023! Step ️1: Register for FHM 2023. Step 2: Follow us on Facebook, Instagram, and LinkedIn. Share your post using #FHM2023 and be sure to tag us! Step 3: Check-in at the checkpoints during FHM 2023! Visit the Recharge Area in Hall 6, Future Hub in Hall 7, & VIP Lounge in Hall 9B. [https://gumtgc.stripocdn.email/content/guids/CABINET_7177af465967c545833e4d898b0eff4727c50fbead8001040f15d30579ff510d/images/social_media_taste_tracker_activity4.jpg] [https://gumtgc.stripocdn.email/content/guids/CABINET_7177af465967c545833e4d898b0eff4727c50fbead8001040f15d30579ff510d/images/mg.png] FHM 2023 – The Gift that Keeps On Giving!
